布鲁斯·韦恩
Bruce Vayne.


12
00:09:08.430 --> 00:09:10.060
布鲁斯·韦恩
Bruce Wayne.


13
00:09:11.550 --> 00:09:14.320
直升机因暴风雨已六天无法降落

14
00:09:14.720 --> 00:09:15.610
他是从哪来的

15
00:09:15.980 --> 00:09:17.610
他说他爬山过来的

16
00:09:18.020 --> 00:09:19.110
不可能

17
00:09:28.080 --> 00:09:29.490
有话快说
Talk.


18
00:09:30.830 --> 00:09:35.330
有个陌生人从大海来到这村庄
I believe there is a stranger. Comes to this village from the sea.


19
00:09:35.500 --> 00:09:38.250
在村民饥寒交迫的严冬到来
He comes in the winter when the people are hungry.


20
00:09:38.420 --> 00:09:40.630
并带来渔获
He brings fish.


21
00:09:40.800 --> 00:09:42.420
他乘着大潮而来
He comes on the king tide.


22
00:09:42.590 --> 00:09:43.840
昨晚的大潮
That was last night.


23
00:09:50.390 --> 00:09:52.680
你也亲眼看见
You have eyes, so see.


24
00:09:52.850 --> 00:09:54.600
渔港结冰
Icebergs in the harbor.


25
00:09:54.770 --> 00:09:56.770
四个月没有船只进港
It's four months since the last ship got through.


26
00:09:57.940 --> 00:10:01.980
这个陌生人不是乘船而来
Well, this stranger doesn't come by ship.


27
00:10:08.950 --> 00:10:12.580
来自远方的敌人即将来袭
There are enemies coming from far away.


28
00:10:13.870 --> 00:10:15.540
我需要战士
I need warriors.


29
00:10:15.710 --> 00:10:19.250
对付这个陌生人 还有像他的其他人
This stranger, others like him.


30
00:10:19.420 --> 00:10:22.920
我要成立一个捍卫地球的联盟
I'm building an alliance to defend ourselves.


31
00:10:23.840 --> 00:10:26.760
我必须见到这个人
It's very important that I see this man.


32
00:10:27.930 --> 00:10:30.220
如果真有这个人
If this stranger exists,


33
00:10:30.390 --> 00:10:32.470
他会把你的话传给他
he'll give him your message.


34
00:10:32.640 --> 00:10:33.850
五千美元
$5,000 American.


35
00:10:34.020 --> 00:10:38.480
我给你两万五 让我和他说话 到外面说去
Look, I'll give you $25,000 to talk to this man right now, outside.


36
00:10:50.820 --> 00:10:55.200
这只狗竟敢把我们当成小孩子
How dare this dog speak to us like children.


37
00:10:56.040 --> 00:10:59.670
什么来自大海的神奇人物
Ooh, magical man from the sea.


38
00:10:59.830 --> 00:11:02.540
我们很穷 但并不蠢
We are poor, not stupid.


39
00:11:02.840 --> 00:11:04.550
滚出去
Get out.


40
00:11:05.670 --> 00:11:06.920
抱歉
I'm sorry.


41
00:11:07.340 --> 00:11:08.880
办不到
Can't do that.


42
00:11:09.130 --> 00:11:11.260
我们说完话我就走
I'll leave after we've spoken.


43
00:11:16.060 --> 00:11:17.480
他叫你"滚出去"
He said, "Get out."


44
00:11:18.250 --> 00:11:20.460
办不到

45
00:11:36.500 --> 00:11:38.370
亚瑟·库瑞
Arthur Curry.


46
00:11:38.540 --> 00:11:41.290
也被称为大海保护者
Also known as Protector of the Oceans.


47
00:11:42.000 --> 00:11:43.630
海王
The Aquaman.


48
00:11:49.340 --> 00:11:51.050
让我搞清楚
So, let me get this straight.


49
00:11:51.220 --> 00:11:54.720
你打扮成蝙蝠真正的蝙蝠
You do it dressed like a bat? Like an actual bat?


50
00:11:54.890 --> 00:11:56.560
我在哥谭市打拼了20年
Worked for 20 years in Gotham.


51
00:11:56.720 --> 00:11:58.560
那个鸟地方
Oh, that shithole.


52
00:11:58.730 --> 00:12:00.520
决战时刻 我们会需要你
When the fight comes, we'll need you.


53
00:12:00.690 --> 00:12:02.440
-别指望了 蝙蝠侠 -为什么
-Don't count on it, Batman. -Why not?


54
00:12:03.360 --> 00:12:05.190
我不喜欢你跑来挖我的隐私
'Cause I don't like you coming here, digging into my business


55
00:12:05.360 --> 00:12:07.900
干涉我的生活 我只想独自一个人
and getting into my life. I want to be left alone.


56
00:12:08.070 --> 00:12:09.070
所以你才这么做
Is that why you do this?


57
00:12:09.240 --> 00:12:11.320
在这鸟不生蛋的地方帮助这些人
Why you help these people out here in the middle of nowhere?


58
00:12:11.490 --> 00:12:14.950
我读过你的故事 你以为没人知道你的善行
I've read the stories. Your good deeds you think no one sees.


59
00:12:15.120 --> 00:12:16.580
你会加入我们
You'll join us.


60
00:12:16.740 --> 00:12:18.450
"强者是孤独的"
"Strong man is strongest alone."


61
00:12:18.620 --> 00:12:19.870
没听过这句话吗
You ever heard that?


62
00:12:20.330 --> 00:12:21.710
你听过超人吗
You ever hear of Superman?


63
00:12:21.870 --> 00:12:23.420
他和我并肩作战时死去
He died fighting next to me.


64
00:12:24.790 --> 00:12:26.170
这正是我的意思
My point exactly.


65
00:12:26.340 --> 00:12:29.760
他相信团结力量大 这是我们欠他的
He believed we were stronger together. We owe it to him.


66
00:12:30.380 --> 00:12:32.630
我谁也不欠
I don't owe anyone anything.


67
00:12:40.310 --> 00:12:42.190
打扮成一只蝙蝠
Dressed like a bat.


68
00:12:43.060 --> 00:12:44.900
你疯了 布鲁斯·韦恩
You're out of your mind, Bruce Wayne.


69
00:14:13.440 --> 00:14:14.650
过去 小灰
Move over, Dusty.


70
00:14:31.460 --> 00:14:36.470
克拉克·乔瑟夫·肯特

71
00:14:46.450 --> 00:14:50.860
法拍屋出售

72
00:15:10.580 --> 00:15:13.630
天啊 韦恩少爷 这里好冷
My God, Master Wayne, but this is cold.


73
00:15:13.800 --> 00:15:18.130
也许我们可以赶上下一波牙买加的大潮
Maybe we can catch the next king tide in Jamaica?


74
00:15:18.300 --> 00:15:20.550
也许斐济一 两个超人类
Might be a metahuman or two in Fiji.


75
00:15:20.720 --> 00:15:22.350
哥斯达黎加天气也不错
Costa Rica's nice.


76
00:15:22.510 --> 00:15:23.930
我找到他了
I found him.


77
00:15:26.810 --> 00:15:28.270
他拒绝了
He said no.


78
00:15:29.270 --> 00:15:31.360
你连一个新兵都没招到
So the draft stands at naught for two?


79
00:15:33.820 --> 00:15:36.570
也许一个成天窝在洞穴的人
Maybe a man who broods in a cave for a living


80
00:15:36.740 --> 00:15:40.240
不适合当招募者
isn't cut out to be a recruiter. Hmm?


81
00:15:59.930 --> 00:16:01.680
十块钱
That's $10, please.


82
00:16:21.990 --> 00:16:25.870
星球日报 每日报导星球事务

83
00:16:29.460 --> 00:16:30.870
曼哈顿银行诚征建筑师

84
00:16:31.630 --> 00:16:34.250
大都会警局

85
00:16:39.880 --> 00:16:40.840
早安 莱恩小姐
Good morning, Miss Lane.


86
00:16:41.010 --> 00:16:42.300
你好 杰瑞
Jerry, hi.


87
00:16:45.220 --> 00:16:46.470
你每天都来 对吧
You don't miss a day, do you?


88
00:16:47.930 --> 00:16:49.890
我喜欢这里
Like it here.


89
00:18:35.710 --> 00:18:36.710
站住
Excuse me.


90
00:18:38.210 --> 00:18:39.210
快上
Move!


91
00:18:49.970 --> 00:18:51.390
快走 快走
Move it! Move it!


92
00:18:57.690 --> 00:18:59.770
-别开枪 -快走
-No, mate, don't shoot! -Move, move!


93
00:19:00.440 --> 00:19:01.940
给我过去
Get the fuck over there!


94
00:19:16.120 --> 00:19:18.080
让他们靠墙站好
Line them up along the wall.


95
00:19:18.250 --> 00:19:19.790
叫他们闭嘴
Keep them quiet.


96
00:19:21.130 --> 00:19:23.420
-安静 -闭嘴
-Keep quiet! -Shut up! Shut up!


97
00:19:23.590 --> 00:19:24.960
叫他们闭嘴
Shut them up too!


98
00:19:28.090 --> 00:19:30.590
我们很快就会发表声明
We'll be making a statement shortly.


99
00:19:30.760 --> 00:19:32.600
在那之前 谁敢乱来
Until then, if I see any movement,


100
00:19:32.760 --> 00:19:34.720
就会害死一大堆小孩
you'll have a lot of dead kids on your hands.


101
00:19:49.780 --> 00:19:51.320
要射杀他吗
Should I take him?


102
00:19:51.490 --> 00:19:53.080
别开枪
Hold your fire.


103
00:19:54.660 --> 00:19:55.700
里面有小孩
They've got kids in there.


104
00:19:57.660 --> 00:19:59.410
他不是虚张声势 长官
Yeah, he's not bluffing, chief.


105
00:19:59.580 --> 00:20:01.790
圣布丽姬中学今天有校外教学
St. Brigid's had a school trip today.


106
00:20:25.820 --> 00:20:26.650
安静
Quiet!


107
00:20:26.820 --> 00:20:27.690
闭嘴
Shut up!


108
00:20:32.780 --> 00:20:35.080
让现代世界崩塌
Down with the modern world.


109
00:20:35.240 --> 00:20:36.790
回到黑暗时代
Back to the Dark Ages.


110
00:20:42.210 --> 00:20:43.290
闭嘴
Quiet!


111
00:20:45.250 --> 00:20:47.920
我叫你们闭嘴
I said shut your fucking mouth.


112
00:21:02.100 --> 00:21:03.770
你是谁
-Who are you?


113
00:21:03.940 --> 00:21:06.770
真言套索会迫使你说实话
The Lasso of Hestia compels you to reveal the truth.


114
00:21:07.520 --> 00:21:09.070
你们是什么人
Now, who are you?


115
00:21:09.690 --> 00:21:12.700
我们是一群反动恐怖份子
We're a small group of reactionary terrorists


116
00:21:12.860 --> 00:21:14.490
要让欧洲倒退到…
who wanna turn back the clock in Europe


117
00:21:14.660 --> 00:21:16.910
-一千年前 -无聊 为何挟持人质
-a thousand years. -Boring. Why the hostages?


118
00:21:17.080 --> 00:21:18.660
我们没有任何要求
We have no demands.


119
00:21:18.830 --> 00:21:20.330
只是在动手之前拖延警察
We're just stalling the police while we do it.


120
00:21:20.580 --> 00:21:21.910
你们想做什么
While you do what?


121
00:21:22.660 --> 00:21:26.250
你太迟了 已经开始倒数计时
You're too late. The countdown's already begun.


122
00:21:26.420 --> 00:21:29.880
再过几分钟 四个街区…
In a few minutes, four city blocks...


123
00:21:31.010 --> 00:21:33.220
全世界都会看到
...while the world watches.


124
00:23:13.820 --> 00:23:14.650
不
No!


125
00:23:14.820 --> 00:23:16.860
就像屠宰场里的羔羊
Like lambs to the slaughter.


126
00:24:06.240 --> 00:24:07.330
我不敢相信
I don't believe it.


127
00:24:07.870 --> 00:24:08.790
相信吧
Believe it.


128
00:24:44.450 --> 00:24:47.200
大家没事吧你没事吧
Is everyone all right? Are you okay?


129
00:24:47.450 --> 00:24:49.450
很好 没事了
Good. It's okay.


130
00:24:49.790 --> 00:24:51.870
没事了 你们可以站起来了
It's okay. It's over. You can stand up.


131
00:24:52.040 --> 00:24:53.130
一切都没事
It's all good.


132
00:24:53.500 --> 00:24:54.920
结束了 你还好吧
It's over now. Are you okay?


133
00:24:55.460 --> 00:24:57.590
-没事吧 -很好
-You okay? -Good.


134
00:25:03.260 --> 00:25:04.550
你没事吧 公主
Are you okay, princess?


135
00:25:08.020 --> 00:25:09.810
我有一天能像你一样吗
Can I be like you someday?


136
00:25:11.980 --> 00:25:14.560
你想成为什么样的人都可以
You can be anything you want to be.


137
00:25:16.480 --> 00:25:18.860
来吧 走吧
Come on. Let's go.


138
00:26:01.650 --> 00:26:02.860
今天有任何变化吗
Any changes today?


139
00:26:03.030 --> 00:26:04.490
没有 女王
No, my Queen.


140
00:26:06.200 --> 00:26:07.820
母盒苏醒了
The Mother Box has awoken,


141
00:26:08.280 --> 00:26:10.160
但什么也没发生
yet nothing has happened.


142
00:26:11.370 --> 00:26:13.410
它从始纪元…
It has slept for thousands of years


143
00:26:13.580 --> 00:26:15.540
就沉睡了数千年
since the First Age.


144
00:26:15.710 --> 00:26:17.040
现在为何苏醒
Why did it wake at all?


145
00:26:24.930 --> 00:26:28.100
这是它出现裂缝后第一次静下来
This is the first time it's gone quiet since the crack appeared.


146
00:26:28.260 --> 00:26:30.930
也许它又继续沉睡
Maybe it's going back to sleep.


147
00:26:35.020 --> 00:26:36.730
邪恶永不沉睡
Evil does not sleep.


148
00:26:37.650 --> 00:26:39.060
只会伺机而待
It waits.


149
00:26:41.070 --> 00:26:43.030
有什么要来了
Something is coming.


150
00:26:48.280 --> 00:26:49.780
准备迎敌
Prepare for battle!


151
00:27:15.270 --> 00:27:17.640
亚马逊女战士 各就各位
Amazons, on your marks!


152
00:27:18.020 --> 00:27:19.310
预备
Ready!


153
00:27:44.550 --> 00:27:46.550
守护者
Defenders.


154
00:27:48.220 --> 00:27:52.470
他们无法保护十万个世界
They have failed 100,000 worlds.


155
00:27:52.970 --> 00:27:54.470
永远都会失败
They always fail.


156
00:27:56.430 --> 00:28:01.100
我是来让你们见识伟大的黑暗
I've come to enlighten you to the great darkness.


157
00:28:01.270 --> 00:28:04.190
我将沉浸在你们的恐惧中
I will bathe in your fear.


158
00:28:05.690 --> 00:28:08.150
天堂岛的女儿
Daughters of Themyscira,


159
00:28:09.490 --> 00:28:11.070
让他看到你们的恐惧
show him your fear!


160
00:28:11.240 --> 00:28:13.660
我们无畏无惧
We have no fear!


161
00:28:32.930 --> 00:28:34.550
召集军团
Gather the legions!


162
00:28:35.470 --> 00:28:36.640
跟她去
Go with her!


163
00:28:36.810 --> 00:28:37.930
你必须封住山洞
You must seal the cage!


164
00:28:38.100 --> 00:28:38.930
快去
-Go!


165
00:28:39.390 --> 00:28:40.520
菲莉普斯
-Phillipus!


166
00:29:07.250 --> 00:29:08.340
不
No!


167
00:29:29.440 --> 00:29:30.610
伊琵欧妮
Epione.


168
00:29:32.530 --> 00:29:34.620
让我们光荣战死 这是对的
Honor us. It's right.


169
00:29:37.580 --> 00:29:38.910
封住大门
Seal it.


170
00:29:44.170 --> 00:29:46.790
拿起大锤
Ready the hammers!


171
00:29:59.010 --> 00:30:00.810
快封住它
Seal it now!


172
00:31:35.530 --> 00:31:37.200
用生命守护它
Guard it with your life.


173
00:31:37.360 --> 00:31:39.160
-遵命 我的女王 -让它保持移动
-Yes, my Queen. -Keep it moving.


174
00:34:25.200 --> 00:34:26.740
拿到了 快走
Got it! Go!


175
00:34:49.640 --> 00:34:53.850
高贵的女王 你为何抗拒
Oh, noble Queen. Why do you fight?


176
00:34:56.900 --> 00:34:58.650
你救不了她
You can't save her.


177
00:34:58.810 --> 00:35:01.270
你救不了任何人
You can't save any of them.


178
00:35:04.780 --> 00:35:08.200
伟大的黑暗即将降临
The great darkness begins.


179
00:35:08.990 --> 00:35:10.330
亚马逊女战士
Amazons!


180
00:35:20.920 --> 00:35:23.590
是的 我们会找到其他的
Yes, we will find the others.


181
00:35:25.470 --> 00:35:26.800
拉弓
-Draw!


182
00:35:30.140 --> 00:35:31.640
放箭
Loose!


183
00:36:29.360 --> 00:36:31.450
他回到了他的宇宙
He's gone back to his universe.


184
00:36:31.620 --> 00:36:32.450
不
No.


185
00:36:35.040 --> 00:36:37.410
他去了人类的世界
He's gone to the lands of men


186
00:36:37.580 --> 00:36:39.710
寻找另外两个母盒
to find the other two boxes.


187
00:36:40.920 --> 00:36:43.250
我们必须点燃古老的警示烽火
We have to light the ancient warning fire.


188
00:36:44.130 --> 00:36:47.590
烽火五千年未曾燃烧
The fire has not burned for 5,000 years.


189
00:36:47.760 --> 00:36:49.300
人类不会知道它的意义
Men won't know what it means.


190
00:36:50.130 --> 00:36:51.510
人类不会知道
Men won't.


191
00:36:53.260 --> 00:36:54.680
她会知道
She will.


192
00:37:00.340 --> 00:37:05.620
第二章

193
00:37:02.980 --> 00:37:05.620
英雄时代

194
00:37:25.420 --> 00:37:28.050
这里是有毒的
It's toxic.


195
00:37:28.210 --> 00:37:29.920
很好
That's good.


196
00:37:50.860 --> 00:37:52.070
去吧
Go!


197
00:37:52.240 --> 00:37:54.240
跟着母盒的气味
Follow the scent of the Mother Boxes.


198
00:37:54.410 --> 00:37:55.950
找到另外两个
Find the missing two.


199
00:37:56.120 --> 00:38:00.000
一旦找到它们 就能形成三位一体
Once they are found, The Unity will be formed.


200
00:38:00.160 --> 00:38:02.910
这个世界将加入其他世界
This world will join the others.


201
00:38:04.830 --> 00:38:06.840
他会很高兴
He will be pleased.


202
00:38:07.000 --> 00:38:09.920
再次看到我的价值
He will see my worth again.


203
00:38:14.510 --> 00:38:17.100
有酒类专卖店那小鬼的消息吗
Anything on that kid from the liquor store?


204
00:38:17.260 --> 00:38:18.680
可能有
Possibly.


205
00:38:19.470 --> 00:38:20.640
"可能有"
"Possibly."


206
00:38:21.850 --> 00:38:24.390
每听一次这句话
If I had a dollar for every "possibly."


207
00:38:24.560 --> 00:38:27.190
就会让我更受不了你
Yeah, it would make you even more insufferable.


208
00:38:30.150 --> 00:38:32.860
脸部辨识可能找到匹配
Facial scan might have got a hit on him,


209
00:38:33.030 --> 00:38:34.860
搞消失的那小子
our disappearing man.


210
00:38:35.490 --> 00:38:40.200
中城的巴里·艾伦先生
One Mr. Barry Allen from Central City.


211
00:38:40.370 --> 00:38:43.290
也许又是误判 你得给我多点时间
Might be another false positive, you'll have to give me a little time


212
00:38:43.460 --> 00:38:45.670
-才能确认 -我们没有时间了
-to confirm. -We don't have any more time.


213
00:38:47.380 --> 00:38:49.130
韦恩少爷
Master Wayne,


214
00:38:49.290 --> 00:38:52.800
你一直在拼命地创建这个团队
you've been working as if there's no tomorrow to build this team


215
00:38:52.970 --> 00:38:54.800
但却找不到任何队友
of people you can't even find.


216
00:38:54.970 --> 00:38:57.090
我找到一个 是两个 包括戴安娜
I found one. I found two, including Diana.


217
00:38:57.260 --> 00:39:01.220
就因为莱克斯·卢瑟说 地球会受到攻击
Just because Lex Luthor says the planet's in danger of attack?


218
00:39:01.390 --> 00:39:03.390
这跟莱克斯·卢瑟无关
This has nothing to do with Lex Luthor.


219
00:39:03.560 --> 00:39:04.770
这跟他有关
It has to do with him.


220
00:39:05.060 --> 00:39:08.360
我在他的坟上向他承诺
I made a promise to him on his grave.


221
00:39:09.230 --> 00:39:12.360
我花了很多时间试图造成分裂
I spent a lot of time trying to divide us.


222
00:39:12.530 --> 00:39:15.320
现在必须团结一心才能拯救地球
I need to bring us together and make this right.


223
00:39:16.110 --> 00:39:18.700
卢瑟的警告已经过了一段时间
Well, it's been some time since Luthor's warning.


224
00:39:18.950 --> 00:39:22.080
没有攻击 没有野蛮人冲进大门
No attacks. No barbarians at the gate.


225
00:39:23.330 --> 00:39:25.960
也许这些野蛮人不走大门
Maybe these barbarians don't use a gate.


226
00:39:26.830 --> 00:39:28.500
也许他们已经来了
Maybe they're already here.


227
00:39:32.500 --> 00:39:34.260
继续找 还有什么线索
Keep looking. What else do you have?


228
00:40:13.250 --> 00:40:14.800
实验室是你的了 霍华德
Lab's all yours, Howard.


229
00:40:14.960 --> 00:40:16.550
11点半

230
00:40:16.720 --> 00:40:18.050
今晚很早嘛 塞拉斯
Early night for you, Silas.


231
00:40:18.220 --> 00:40:20.300
是啊 我提早下班
Yes, early night.


232
00:40:20.970 --> 00:40:22.100
替我向你家人问好
Tell your family I said hello.


233
00:40:57.460 --> 00:40:59.050
搞什么…
What the...


234
00:41:02.970 --> 00:41:04.140
天啊
Jesus.


235
00:42:17.380 --> 00:42:19.210
阿提密斯之箭
The Arrow of Artemis.


236
00:42:20.300 --> 00:42:22.840
它将射到人类世界
It will reach the lands of men.


237
00:42:32.480 --> 00:42:33.770
天空火炬
Sky torch,


238
00:42:33.940 --> 00:42:35.480
英雄烽火
hero beacon,


239
00:42:35.650 --> 00:42:37.360
驱散黑暗
scatter the darkness.


240
00:42:37.520 --> 00:42:40.780
如昔日一般熊熊燃烧
Burn as you burned in days before.


241
00:42:42.360 --> 00:42:45.820
让她看到历史曙光出现之前的黑暗
Show her the darkness before the daylight of history.


242
00:42:46.320 --> 00:42:49.910
警告我女儿战争已经来临
Warn my daughter that war has come


243
00:42:51.290 --> 00:42:53.000
并且保护她
and protect her.


244
00:43:17.730 --> 00:43:20.020
回到我身边 戴安娜
Return to me, Diana.


245
00:43:58.650 --> 00:44:01.270
你这周末做什么了 戴安娜
What did you do this weekend, Diana?


246
00:44:01.610 --> 00:44:03.940
没做什么特别的
Nothing very interesting.


247
00:44:04.940 --> 00:44:07.030
你每次都这么说
That's all you ever tell us.


248
00:44:07.650 --> 00:44:10.160
没办法 我的生活很无趣
What can I do? I'm not that exciting.


249
00:44:10.320 --> 00:44:13.790
你一走出去就好像消失一样
You might as well disappear when you walk out of here.


250
00:44:18.670 --> 00:44:19.670
又来了
Again?


251
00:44:19.830 --> 00:44:21.710
-什么事 -又怎么了
-What is it? -Now what?


252
00:44:22.090 --> 00:44:25.210
预算缩减 盗墓者
Budget cuts, tomb raiders.


253
00:44:25.380 --> 00:44:27.880
现在又加了一条"纵火者"
Now add to the list "arson."


254
00:44:29.760 --> 00:44:32.390
记者在克里特岛连线报导
Yes, good morning From the isle of Crete.


255
00:44:32.550 --> 00:44:37.100
我身后的大篝火熊熊燃烧
As you can see behind me, an enormous bonfire is burning.


256
00:44:37.270 --> 00:44:39.390
大火燃烧了一整晚
This fire has been burning through the night.


257
00:44:39.560 --> 00:44:43.360
现在已经是早上 我们至少在八公里以外
We're now into the morning and we are at least five miles away.


258
00:44:43.520 --> 00:44:46.860
但还是能看到它在燃烧
And we can still see it burning as we speak.


259
00:44:47.030 --> 00:44:50.070
当地居民和政府当局都感到诧异
This has baffled locals and government authorities alike


260
00:44:50.240 --> 00:44:54.740
这座历史遗迹亚马逊神殿居然起火
here at this historical site of the so-called shrine of the Amazons.


261
00:44:54.910 --> 00:44:56.410
-当地居民和政府当局… -敌人入侵
Now, locals and government officials are baffled as to


262
00:44:56.580 --> 00:44:58.870
…不知道火势起因
-what may have caused this. -Invasion.


263
00:45:08.010 --> 00:45:09.050
瑞恩
Ryan.


264
00:45:09.220 --> 00:45:10.590
-你好 博士 -那个…
-Hiya, Doc. -Is the...


265
00:45:10.760 --> 00:45:12.590
电子激光没有损坏
No damage to the electron-laser.


266
00:45:12.890 --> 00:45:14.930
-塞拉斯·斯通博士 -是的
-Uh, Dr. Silas Stone? -Yeah.


267
00:45:15.100 --> 00:45:16.180
-蔡瑞恩 -是的
-Ryan Choi? -That's us.


268
00:45:17.640 --> 00:45:19.390
这是谁干的 他们有没有偷走什么
Um, who did this? Did they steal anything?


269
00:45:19.560 --> 00:45:21.600
-他们偷走了一切 -那个呢
They took whatever was in here. That?


270
00:45:21.770 --> 00:45:24.190
那没被偷走 对吧 斯通博士
Oh, that wasn't stolen. Was it, Dr. Stone?


271
00:45:25.150 --> 00:45:27.480
对 那之前就被移走了
No. That was misplaced a while ago.


272
00:45:28.070 --> 00:45:31.910
6-1-9-8-2号物件 国防部档案馆
Object 6-1-9-8-2. Department of Defense Archives.


273
00:45:32.950 --> 00:45:33.870
那是什么
What was it?


274
00:45:34.280 --> 00:45:35.200
我也不知道
I don't know.


275
00:45:35.370 --> 00:45:36.290
你不知道
You don't know?


276
00:45:36.450 --> 00:45:38.700
没错 所以我才在研究它
I don't know, which was why I was studying it.


277
00:45:38.870 --> 00:45:40.370
你是什么官阶
What's your rank, Doctor?


278
00:45:40.790 --> 00:45:42.790
瑞恩 麻烦你了
Ryan, would you, uh, do the honors?


279
00:45:42.960 --> 00:45:44.290
-没问题 -谢了
-Sure. Okay. -Thanks.


280
00:45:44.460 --> 00:45:45.290
平民
Civilian.


281
00:45:45.630 --> 00:45:48.340
星辰实验室是私人承包商 我们为国防部工作
STARLABS is a private contractor. We work for the DoD.


282
00:45:48.510 --> 00:45:51.090
为他们提供异常科学的建议
We advise them on xeno-science.


283
00:45:51.630 --> 00:45:52.470
"异常科学"
"Xeno-science"?


284
00:45:53.140 --> 00:45:54.970
外星科技
Alien technology.


285
00:46:02.060 --> 00:46:04.150
比如说
For example,


286
00:46:04.310 --> 00:46:05.860
超人飞船
the Superman ship.


287
00:46:14.360 --> 00:46:17.080
昨晚有八个人没离开实验室
Eight people never signed out of the lab last night, Doctor.


288
00:46:17.450 --> 00:46:20.500
清洁工 警卫和几名研究科学家
Cleaning staff, guards, a few of your research scientists.


289
00:46:20.950 --> 00:46:21.870
他们被绑架了
They were abducted.


290
00:46:23.250 --> 00:46:24.250
你确定
Are you sure?


291
00:46:24.420 --> 00:46:26.960
有位目击证人 他逃过一劫
Witness saw it all. He escaped.


292
00:46:27.130 --> 00:46:30.260
他正在隔离区协助绘制嫌犯肖像画
He's here in quarantine now, working on an ID sketch.


293
00:46:33.260 --> 00:46:37.600
知道那会是谁或是什么东西吗
Any idea who or what that might be?


294
00:46:57.740 --> 00:46:59.790
母盒在这里不安全
The box isn't safe here.


295
00:47:02.290 --> 00:47:03.750
维克多
Victor,


296
00:47:03.960 --> 00:47:06.210
他们闯进实验室找它
they came looking for it at the lab.


297
00:47:06.380 --> 00:47:10.800
有些人被某种怪物抓走
People were taken by some kind of monster or something.


298
00:47:13.550 --> 00:47:15.510
你对怪物很了解…
You know a lot about monsters,


299
00:47:16.130 --> 00:47:17.550
对吧
don't you?


300
00:47:23.930 --> 00:47:26.060
尤其是怎么制造它们
Especially how to make 'em.


301
00:50:26.660 --> 00:50:30.290
求救…求救…
Mayday! Mayday, mayday!


302
00:50:31.080 --> 00:50:34.170
船身受损 我快沉下去了
My hull is breached. I'm going down.


303
00:50:40.510 --> 00:50:42.470
求救
Mayday!


304
00:50:42.670 --> 00:50:44.720
有人吗
Is there anybody out there?


305
00:51:25.050 --> 00:51:26.390
威士忌
Whiskey.


306
00:51:35.480 --> 00:51:38.060
下次叫他要敬畏暴风雨
Tell him to respect the storm next time.


307
00:51:47.410 --> 00:51:48.240
他请客
It's on him.


308
00:54:16.470 --> 00:54:18.560
本应是国王的男人
King who would be man.


309
00:54:18.720 --> 00:54:21.890
人类父亲和海洋女王的儿子
Son of a human father and Queen of the Seas.


310
00:54:22.770 --> 00:54:24.520
我浪费了多少时间
All the time I've wasted


311
00:54:24.690 --> 00:54:27.730
试图遵守我向你母亲做的承诺
trying to keep the promise I made to your mother.


312
00:54:29.860 --> 00:54:31.070
说完了吗 老头
Are you finished, old man?


313
00:54:31.240 --> 00:54:33.700
虽然你居无定所
You never sleep in the same place twice,


314
00:54:33.860 --> 00:54:36.620
但还是一直回来这里
yet you keep coming back here.


315
00:54:38.580 --> 00:54:40.540
我喜欢这里 很安静
I like it. It's quiet.


316
00:54:40.700 --> 00:54:42.500
这是你继承的王国
It's your inheritance.


317
00:54:42.660 --> 00:54:44.790
你应当是亚特兰蒂斯国王
You're the rightful king of Atlantis.


318
00:54:45.920 --> 00:54:47.040
我们的同胞受苦受难
Our people suffer.


319
00:54:47.210 --> 00:54:49.170
你的同胞
Your people.


320
00:54:49.340 --> 00:54:52.880
一个卑鄙残忍 迷信无知的种族
A brutal, petty, superstitious race.


321
00:54:53.050 --> 00:54:54.260
地表有什么不同吗
Is the surface any different?


322
00:54:55.340 --> 00:54:57.390
没人说我是地表之王
Nobody calls me King of the Surface.


323
00:54:58.470 --> 00:55:00.180
你想要什么 维科
What do you want, Vulko?


324
00:55:00.770 --> 00:55:03.640
要塞附近的守卫不断消失不见
Guards near the stronghold have been disappearing.


325
00:55:03.810 --> 00:55:05.230
来自天上的掠夺者
Snatchers from above.


326
00:55:05.400 --> 00:55:06.610
去跟欧姆国王说啊
Talk to King Orm.


327
00:55:06.770 --> 00:55:08.190
-你弟弟 -表弟
-Your brother? -Half-brother.


328
00:55:08.360 --> 00:55:11.360
他想煽动和陆地人类的战争
He's trying to fan the flames of war with the surface.


329
00:55:11.740 --> 00:55:13.150
他说谎
He lies.


330
00:55:14.610 --> 00:55:18.620
掠夺者来自黑暗之境 他们在寻找它
The snatchers have come from the dark place. They're looking for it.


331
00:55:19.450 --> 00:55:22.790
我们守护的母盒并不安全
The Mother Box our people guard is not safe.


332
00:55:23.790 --> 00:55:27.790
前往亚特兰蒂斯要塞 保护母盒
Go to the stronghold of Atlantis. Protect the box.


333
00:55:28.790 --> 00:55:30.000
时候到了
The time has come.


334
00:55:32.130 --> 00:55:34.130
把你母亲的三叉戟拿去
Take up your mother's trident.


335
00:55:45.310 --> 00:55:48.980
你不能永远弃世界而不顾 亚瑟
You can't turn your back on the world forever, Arthur.


336
00:55:49.900 --> 00:55:52.990
不管是地表或海底
Above or below.


337
00:56:22.100 --> 00:56:23.680
狄萨德
DeSaad.


338
00:56:23.850 --> 00:56:27.810
狄萨德 我呼叫你
DeSaad! I call to thee.


339
00:56:36.860 --> 00:56:41.030
荒原狼 你开始征服这世界了吗
Steppenwolf, have you begun the conquest?


340
00:56:42.160 --> 00:56:44.540
这个世界是分裂的
This world is divided.


341
00:56:45.330 --> 00:56:46.830
他们是原始物种
They are a primitive species.


342
00:56:47.000 --> 00:56:49.330
未进化并与彼此战争
Unevolved and at war with one another.


343
00:56:49.500 --> 00:56:52.340
歧见太深无法团结一心
Too separate to be one.


344
00:56:52.500 --> 00:56:56.760
必须像其他的世界一样 剥夺他们的自由意志
Their free will must be ripped from them, like the other worlds.


345
00:56:56.920 --> 00:57:01.050
并以服膺他的光荣信念…
Given absolution in one glorious belief,


346
00:57:01.220 --> 00:57:02.930
获得赦免
to serve him.


347
00:57:03.720 --> 00:57:05.640
母盒呢
The Mother Boxes?


348
00:57:06.220 --> 00:57:09.140
我找到其中一个
I have found one of the three.


349
00:57:09.310 --> 00:57:11.770
苏醒后呼唤我的那一个
The one that woke and called to me.


350
00:57:11.940 --> 00:57:13.440
另外两个仍然沉睡
The other two still sleep,


351
00:57:13.610 --> 00:57:17.440
但天启魔感应到它们
but the parademons feel their presence.


352
00:57:17.610 --> 00:57:19.070
它们飞来飞去
They fly,


353
00:57:19.240 --> 00:57:22.820
到处搜索 并抓走带有母盒气味的囚犯
they search, they take prisoners who carry the scent,


354
00:57:22.990 --> 00:57:27.910
我则以他之名创建一座要塞
while I build a stronghold in the name of his glory.


355
00:57:28.460 --> 00:57:30.330
很好
Yes.


356
00:57:31.420 --> 00:57:34.090
强大的荒原狼
Mighty Steppenwolf,


357
00:57:35.590 --> 00:57:39.970
你本来可以与伟大的他平起平坐
who might have sat here by the side of the great one.


358
00:57:41.890 --> 00:57:46.470
但却因自大而被放逐
But undone by his self-pride.


359
00:57:47.640 --> 00:57:49.020
狄萨德
DeSaad...


360
00:57:50.100 --> 00:57:52.480
我跪倒在你面前
I fall before you.


361
00:57:53.230 --> 00:57:55.020
让我向他求情
Let me make a plea to him


362
00:57:55.190 --> 00:57:57.110
当我以他之名夺下这世界
that I may come home


363
00:57:57.280 --> 00:58:00.070
能否请他让我回家
after I take this world in his name.


364
00:58:00.240 --> 00:58:02.660
你背叛了他
You betrayed him.


365
00:58:04.070 --> 00:58:05.580
你自己的家人
Your own family.


366
00:58:05.740 --> 00:58:07.950
我看到我犯的错误
I saw my mistake.


367
00:58:08.120 --> 00:58:10.710
我屠杀企图争夺他王位的人
I slaughtered those who sought his throne.


368
00:58:10.870 --> 00:58:16.000
你还欠他五万个世界
You still owe the great one 50,000 more worlds.


369
00:58:17.090 --> 00:58:18.920
当你还清了债
He will hear your plea


370
00:58:19.380 --> 00:58:21.630
他就会聆听你的恳求
when you pay your debt.


371
00:58:24.550 --> 00:58:27.600
母盒将被寻获并合而为一
The Mother Boxes will be found and united.


372
00:58:28.560 --> 00:58:30.680
这里没有保护者
No protectors here.


373
00:58:30.850 --> 00:58:34.270
没有绿光战警 没有氪星人
No Lanterns, no Kryptonian.


374
00:58:34.440 --> 00:58:38.070
这世界将会像其他的一样沦陷
This world will fall, like all the others.


375
00:58:39.110 --> 00:58:40.860
为了达克赛德
For Darkseid.


376
00:58:44.070 --> 00:58:46.280
为了达克赛德
For Darkseid.


377
00:59:07.550 --> 00:59:11.140
我花了几百万元安装保全系统
You know, I paid millions of dollars for this building's security.


378
00:59:11.310 --> 00:59:12.600
钱花得很值得
You got your money's worth.


379
00:59:13.100 --> 00:59:15.480
我几乎花了一分钟才解除
Took me almost a minute to disable it.


380
00:59:17.020 --> 00:59:18.360
你好
Hi there.


381
00:59:20.190 --> 00:59:21.030
新玩具
A new toy?


382
00:59:21.940 --> 00:59:24.110
原型军队运输机
Prototype troop carrier.


383
00:59:26.410 --> 00:59:29.450
我曾相识的一个人会很想开开看
I once knew a man who would have loved to fly it.


384
00:59:30.080 --> 00:59:33.040
韦恩航天最顶尖的人才 都无法让它飞起来
The best minds at Wayne Aerospace couldn't make it fly.


385
00:59:34.120 --> 00:59:35.710
但是你能
But you can?


386
00:59:35.870 --> 00:59:37.540
我别无选择
I have no choice.


387
00:59:37.710 --> 00:59:40.460
我需要更远的航程和更大的货舱
I need more range and I need more cargo.


388
00:59:40.630 --> 00:59:42.210
我认为一场攻击即将来袭
I think there's an attack coming.


389
00:59:42.630 --> 00:59:44.380
你错了 布鲁斯
Not coming, Bruce.


390
00:59:45.180 --> 00:59:47.140
它已经来袭了
It's already here.


391
00:59:47.930 --> 00:59:52.470
据我所知 他们来自另一个宇宙
From what I've learned, they are things from another universe.


392
00:59:52.640 --> 00:59:54.980
为一个黑暗力量效忠
They serve a dark power.


393
00:59:55.140 --> 00:59:56.850
一个古老的力量
An old power.


394
00:59:57.020 --> 00:59:58.440
他们想要什么
What do they want?


395
00:59:59.270 --> 01:00:01.610
入侵地球 征服世界
To invade. To conquer.


396
01:00:02.730 --> 01:00:06.990
他们很久以前曾经来过
They came here once before, long ago.


397
01:00:12.120 --> 01:00:14.540
一支庞大的舰队出现在天空
A great armada appeared in the sky,


398
01:00:14.710 --> 01:00:17.330
消灭所有胆敢反抗的势力
laying waste to all who opposed it.


399
01:00:17.500 --> 01:00:21.590
入侵者的首领是达克赛德
The leader of the invaders was a being called Darkseid.


400
01:00:21.750 --> 01:00:26.010
这名字在每个宇宙都受到诅咒和畏惧
A name cursed and feared in every universe.


401
01:00:26.880 --> 01:00:30.720
地球的守护者 和达克赛德展开一场大战
Darkseid was met in battle by Earth's defenders.


402
01:00:30.890 --> 01:00:33.390
旧神族 人类
The old gods, men...


403
01:00:33.970 --> 01:00:37.100
被迫迁至海底之前的亚特兰蒂斯族
Atlanteans before their descent into the sea...


404
01:00:39.440 --> 01:00:43.400
遭背叛及被困禁之前的亚马逊族
Amazons before their betrayal and enslavement


405
01:00:43.570 --> 01:00:45.940
以及来自星空的守护者
and guardians from the stars.


406
01:00:46.110 --> 01:00:49.700
他们的历史教导他们 不能相信彼此
Their histories had taught them not to trust each other,


407
01:00:49.870 --> 01:00:52.030
不能奢望创建联盟
not to hope for an alliance.


408
01:00:52.200 --> 01:00:54.200
而是各自奋战
To fight apart.


409
01:01:43.250 --> 01:01:45.960
当达克赛德在地球发动战争
As Darkseid waged war on Earth,


410
01:01:46.130 --> 01:01:47.550
他发现一个秘密
he found a secret there.


411
01:01:47.710 --> 01:01:51.470
隐藏在无垠太空的一股力量
A power hidden in the infinity of space.


412
01:01:51.640 --> 01:01:53.140
他召唤暗黑秘士
He called forth mystics


413
01:01:53.300 --> 01:01:56.430
他们崇拜并控制三个物体
who worshipped and controlled three objects...


414
01:01:56.600 --> 01:01:57.640
母盒
the Mother Boxes.


415
01:01:57.980 --> 01:01:59.390
等等
Wait, wait, wait.


416
01:01:59.560 --> 01:02:00.560
"母盒"
"Mother Boxes"?


417
01:02:00.730 --> 01:02:03.270
坚不可摧 活生生的机器
Indestructible living machines,


418
01:02:03.980 --> 01:02:08.900
使用先进无比的科技打造 看起来简直就像巫术
made from a science so advanced, it looks like sorcery.


419
01:02:09.070 --> 01:02:11.700
若要征服世界 三个母盒必须同步化
To conquer, three boxes have to synchronize


420
01:02:11.860 --> 01:02:15.120
合而为一后形成三位一体
and join together into The Unity.


421
01:02:15.280 --> 01:02:18.330
三位一体以烈火净化星球
The Unity cleanses a planet with fire,


422
01:02:18.500 --> 01:02:22.080
将它转换成另一个敌人世界
transforming it into a copy of the enemy's world.


423
01:02:22.250 --> 01:02:25.750
幸存者都成为达克赛德的仆役
All who live become servants of Darkseid.


424
01:02:25.920 --> 01:02:28.840
活着 但毫无生机
Alive but drained of life.


425
01:02:29.050 --> 01:02:30.380
天启魔
Parademons.


426
01:02:31.590 --> 01:02:33.680
亚马逊女战士
-Amazons!


427
01:02:39.560 --> 01:02:41.270
冲啊
With me!


428
01:03:10.590 --> 01:03:13.090
但在三位一体同步化之前
But before The Unity could synchronize,


429
01:03:13.260 --> 01:03:16.640
地球的守护者组成统一阵线展开反击
the defenders of Earth attacked and fought as one.


430
01:03:17.220 --> 01:03:20.220
亚马逊人和亚特兰蒂斯人并肩作战
Amazons alongside Atlanteans.


431
01:03:20.390 --> 01:03:24.900
宙斯及他儿子阿瑞斯 和来自星空的守护者联手出击
Zeus and his son Ares alongside the guardians from the sky.


432
01:03:25.900 --> 01:03:30.570
一群黄金时代英雄为了捍卫地球 同心协力捍卫了地球的生命
A golden Age of Heroes fighting together to defend life on Earth.


433
01:05:27.230 --> 01:05:30.020
他们做到其他世界做不到的事
They did what no world had ever done.


434
01:05:30.190 --> 01:05:32.360
将敌人送回星空
Sent the enemies back into the stars.


435
01:05:34.900 --> 01:05:38.150
三个母盒从未合而为一
The three Mother Boxes never synchronized.


436
01:05:38.740 --> 01:05:41.910
也从未形成三位一体
-The Unity never came to pass.


437
01:05:42.070 --> 01:05:44.280
但在敌人撤退之时
But, in their retreat,


438
01:05:44.910 --> 01:05:48.040
母盒被留在地球
the boxes were left behind on Earth.


439
01:05:48.210 --> 01:05:51.920
它们的力量变弱 就像失去主人的恶犬
They grew weak. Dogs without masters


440
01:05:53.750 --> 01:05:55.340
开始沉睡
falling asleep,


441
01:05:55.500 --> 01:05:57.970
等待他们的回归
awaiting their return.


442
01:05:58.130 --> 01:06:00.470
母盒从敌人的视野中消失
Fading from the view of the enemy,


443
01:06:00.630 --> 01:06:03.800
隐匿在一兆个世界之中
anonymous among a trillion worlds.


444
01:06:20.700 --> 01:06:23.870
地球的守护者立下誓言
The defenders of Earth made a vow.


445
01:06:24.240 --> 01:06:27.490
人类 亚特兰蒂斯族及亚马逊族
Men, Atlanteans, and Amazons.


446
01:06:27.660 --> 01:06:31.540
根据他们文化的惯例及仪式
Each would enshrine and guard one of the three sleeping Mother Boxes


447
01:06:31.710 --> 01:06:35.210
各自封存并守卫 其中一个沉睡的母盒
according to the rites and rituals of their culture


448
01:06:35.380 --> 01:06:39.840
以防母盒日后再次苏醒 向天启星发出信号
in case a box should ever wake again to call out to the planet Apokolips


449
01:06:40.010 --> 01:06:41.760
呼唤敌人回来并企图征服
to return and conquer


450
01:06:41.930 --> 01:06:45.720
达克赛德唯一落败而逃的世界
the only world Darkseid had ever lost.


451
01:08:01.670 --> 01:08:04.340
有什么唤醒了我的族人守卫的母盒
Something woke the box my people guard.


452
01:08:05.050 --> 01:08:07.090
它向暗黑之处呼唤
It called out to the dark place...


453
01:08:07.260 --> 01:08:09.680
引来达克赛德手下的一名征服者
to one of Darkseid's conquerors.


454
01:08:10.600 --> 01:08:12.470
敌人已经来袭
The enemy is here.


455
01:08:12.980 --> 01:08:14.640
如果是真的 他在哪里
If he's here, where is he?


456
01:08:14.810 --> 01:08:16.900
他会到处寻找另外两个母盒
He'll be searching for the other two boxes.


457
01:08:17.060 --> 01:08:20.020
得到三个母盒并准备好之前 他仍在藏匿
Hiding until he has all three. Until he's ready.


458
01:08:20.190 --> 01:08:24.030
我们必须准备迎敌 你 我和其他人
Then we have to be ready. You, me, the others.


459
01:08:24.780 --> 01:08:27.610
他们说英雄时代不会再来临
They said the Age of Heroes would never come again.


460
01:08:27.780 --> 01:08:29.030
会来的
No, it will.


461
01:08:29.370 --> 01:08:31.080
必须的
It has to.


462
01:08:32.830 --> 01:08:36.330
其他人 他们在哪里
The others. Where are they?


463
01:08:41.420 --> 01:08:46.680
第三章

464
01:08:43.060 --> 01:08:46.680
挚爱的母亲，挚爱的儿子

465
01:08:48.390 --> 01:08:50.260
冷藏配送

466
01:08:50.260 --> 01:08:53.970
中城

467
01:08:53.970 --> 01:08:57.600
前方减速

468
01:08:58.350 --> 01:09:01.020
我迟到了吗 我大迟到了
Am I late? No, I'm so late. I'm very late.


469
01:09:00.390 --> 01:09:02.190
中城狗狗托儿所

470
01:09:02.360 --> 01:09:03.480
你好啊 小家伙
Oh, hey, buddy. Hey.


471
01:09:04.320 --> 01:09:05.150
不行
-Oh. No.


472
01:09:06.240 --> 01:09:07.820
好吧 晚点见
Okay, bye. Okay.


473
01:09:08.700 --> 01:09:10.620
真是拍谢
-I'm so sorry.


474
01:09:11.030 --> 01:09:12.280
我迟到了
I'm late.


475
01:09:17.790 --> 01:09:18.830
-你是… -我…
-Are you, uh... -I'm...


476
01:09:19.000 --> 01:09:21.250
抱歉我大迟到了 不是故意的
I'm so sorry I'm so late. I didn't mean to be so late.


477
01:09:21.420 --> 01:09:22.920
我是我 我来了 很抱歉迟到了
I'm me and I'm here and I'm so sorry I'm late.


478
01:09:23.090 --> 01:09:25.260
因为公车没来 后来来了
Essentially, the bus didn't come, then the bus did come,


479
01:09:25.420 --> 01:09:27.720
不过有个阿婆一直在找硬币
but then there was this old woman counting change for the fare,


480
01:09:27.880 --> 01:09:29.010
五分 一分 五分 一分
like, nickel, penny, nickel, penny.


481
01:09:29.180 --> 01:09:30.930
真是够了 让阿婆上车吧
Like, jeez Louise, let this woman on the bus.


482
01:09:31.090 --> 01:09:32.100
她都107岁了
She's 107 years old,


483
01:09:32.260 --> 01:09:33.930
不会再活多久了
these are some of her last few moments of life.


484
01:09:34.100 --> 01:09:35.140
履历
Resume.


485
01:09:35.770 --> 01:09:36.600
履历
Resume.


486
01:09:39.850 --> 01:09:40.940
拜托
Come on.


487
01:09:44.270 --> 01:09:45.360
拜托
Come on.


488
01:09:45.530 --> 01:09:47.070
那是法文来着
From the French, of course.


489
01:09:47.240 --> 01:09:50.280
"履历"是过去分词…
"Resume," I believe, is a past participle of...


490
01:09:56.120 --> 01:09:57.200
这可不妙
Uh, wow. That's no good.


491
01:09:57.660 --> 01:10:00.870
我的口袋有什么 "有只吃纸的怪物"
It's like, what lives in my pocket, right? "Paper monster hungry." Uh...


492
01:10:09.760 --> 01:10:12.840
拜托 我们应该是朋友啊
Come on. Supposed to be friends now.


493
01:10:19.430 --> 01:10:20.440
好了
-Yes.


494
01:10:29.440 --> 01:10:31.860
中城大学 我念刑事司法系
Central City College, I'm a criminal justice major.


495
01:10:32.030 --> 01:10:34.280
你说你有遛狗的经验
You said you had experience walking dogs.


496
01:13:14.740 --> 01:13:16.780
天啊 希望大家都没事
Oh, gosh, I hope everyone's okay.


497
01:13:16.950 --> 01:13:21.660
瞧 照顾狗狗遇到事情 我一定会随身携带肉类零食
See, in times of crisis, for dog work, I always bring a meat snack.


498
01:13:21.830 --> 01:13:23.080
能让狗狗安静下来
'Cause it makes them feel calm.


499
01:13:23.240 --> 01:13:25.120
你永远不知道会发生什么事
'Cause you never know what's going to happen in this city.


500
01:13:25.290 --> 01:13:27.000
我是说 天啊
I mean, oh, my gosh.


501
01:13:27.160 --> 01:13:29.710
是不是星期一开工吗
Right? I start on Monday?


502
01:14:08.040 --> 01:14:10.710
你一定靠近过母盒
You have been near a Mother Box.


503
01:14:11.920 --> 01:14:13.920
身上有它的气味
The scent is on you.


504
01:14:14.500 --> 01:14:15.750
它在哪里
Where is it?


505
01:14:16.170 --> 01:14:19.050
亚特兰蒂斯族的儿女绝不会告诉你
No son or daughter of Atlantis will ever tell you.


506
01:14:34.650 --> 01:14:37.480
我们的族人看守了母盒数千年
Our people have guarded the Mother Box for thousands of years.


507
01:14:43.660 --> 01:14:46.290
我不会背叛自己的族人
I will never betray my own people.


508
01:14:57.840 --> 01:15:00.340
你已经背叛了
You already have.


509
01:16:00.690 --> 01:16:02.900
这是在地球最深的海沟拍到的
This was taken in the deepest trench on Earth.


510
01:16:03.490 --> 01:16:05.570
他一定是亚特兰蒂斯人
He must be an Atlantean.


511
01:16:05.740 --> 01:16:06.870
能够呼吸海水
A water-breather.


512
01:16:07.030 --> 01:16:08.700
我跟他说话时他呼吸空气
He was breathing air when I talked to him.


513
01:16:08.870 --> 01:16:10.660
那他就是混血儿
Mixed-blood, then.


514
01:16:10.830 --> 01:16:12.700
他说他会和我们一起作战
He said he'll fight with us?


515
01:16:12.870 --> 01:16:14.210
或多或少吧
More or less.


516
01:16:15.580 --> 01:16:17.670
或多还是或少
More more or more less?


517
01:16:18.090 --> 01:16:19.090
大概是或少吧
Probably more less.


518
01:16:19.250 --> 01:16:21.050
-他说不 -没错
-He said no? -He said no.


519
01:16:21.800 --> 01:16:23.220
亚特兰蒂斯人很难搞
Atlanteans can be tricky.


520
01:16:24.130 --> 01:16:26.890
我的族人曾和他们打仗
My people went to war with them once.


521
01:16:28.010 --> 01:16:30.100
我不确定我们能相信他
I'm not sure we can trust him.


522
01:16:30.260 --> 01:16:31.310
戴安娜 如果我们要合作
Diana, if we're gonna do this,


523
01:16:31.470 --> 01:16:33.810
你就得打开心房 接受我们不能…
you're gonna need to be open to more things that we didn't...


524
01:16:33.980 --> 01:16:34.850
你知道的
you know...


525
01:16:35.020 --> 01:16:36.690
-抱歉 没关系 -对不起 我的错
-I'm sorry. That's okay. -Sorry. My fault.


526
01:16:36.850 --> 01:16:37.900
没关系
Don't worry about it.


527
01:16:38.060 --> 01:16:39.310
-让我们… -难免的
-Let's... -It happens.


528
01:16:39.480 --> 01:16:40.360
所以…
-so...


529
01:16:40.520 --> 01:16:42.570
这是第三个人
This is the third person.


530
01:16:42.730 --> 01:16:45.150
消失了1/30秒
Disappears for 1/30 of a second here.


531
01:16:45.320 --> 01:16:46.820
一格的影片 看到吗
One frame of video, see?


532
01:16:46.990 --> 01:16:49.620
中城的巴里·艾伦
Barry Allen. Central City.


533
01:16:49.780 --> 01:16:50.620
你去找他
Go to him.


534
01:16:50.780 --> 01:16:52.490
我去找第四个人
I'll work on number four.


535
01:16:52.660 --> 01:16:55.790
有机与生化机械电子身体器官
Organic and biomechatronic body parts.


536
01:16:58.330 --> 01:17:00.340
他是个钢骨生化人
He's a cyborg.


537
01:17:18.480 --> 01:17:19.310
斯通

538
01:17:19.480 --> 01:17:21.440
-预备 -就位
-Ready! -Break!


539
01:17:22.480 --> 01:17:24.900
大声尖叫

540
01:17:36.960 --> 01:17:37.960
3
Three...


541
01:17:38.330 --> 01:17:39.880
80
eighty...


542
01:17:40.960 --> 01:17:43.050
预备…上吧
set... go!


543
01:17:56.310 --> 01:17:58.560
你儿子也许是美式足球校队队长
Your son may be captain of the football team


544
01:17:58.730 --> 01:18:01.730
也是个天才 斯通太太
and a certified genius, Mrs. Stone...


545
01:18:01.900 --> 01:18:03.980
斯通博士
Dr. Stone.


546
01:18:06.530 --> 01:18:08.530
但不代表他能骇入校方系统
...but that doesn't mean he can hack into our system


547
01:18:08.700 --> 01:18:10.530
窜改他同学的成绩
to change his friend's grades.


548
01:18:11.490 --> 01:18:14.830
莎拉一家人今年失去了房子
Sarah's family lost their house this year.


549
01:18:15.410 --> 01:18:17.830
那孩子怎么可能及格
How could that child pass her classes?


550
01:18:19.410 --> 01:18:22.460
维克多是出于好心才会帮助她
Victor helped her 'cause he's got a good heart.


551
01:18:22.630 --> 01:18:24.670
你又做了什么来帮助她
What did you do to help her?


552
01:18:39.600 --> 01:18:42.530
哥谭市 威斯康星州

553
01:19:48.800 --> 01:19:51.720
-你爸… -妈 别说了
