01:35:26.650 --> 01:35:28.400
当然是黑色的罗
-In black, of course. -Oh.


737
01:35:36.240 --> 01:35:39.200
好吧 维克多斯通
-All right. Victor Stone.


738
01:35:39.280 --> 01:35:43.670
搜寻维克多·斯通

739
01:35:55.470 --> 01:35:57.470
有点不对劲
Something is not working.


740
01:36:01.720 --> 01:36:03.400
在这里见面 现在

741
01:36:09.280 --> 01:36:11.700
看来你有个约会 普林斯小姐
Looks like you have a date, Miss Prince.


742
01:37:08.750 --> 01:37:11.840
你为什么找我 戴安娜
Why are you looking for me, Diana?


743
01:37:12.010 --> 01:37:13.260
你知道我是谁
You know who I am.


744
01:37:13.420 --> 01:37:15.760
我知道的远远超乎你想像
I know more than you can possibly imagine.


745
01:37:15.930 --> 01:37:18.510
那也许你已经知道我需要你的帮助
Then maybe you already know I need your help.


746
01:37:19.180 --> 01:37:20.180
全世界都需要
The world does.


747
01:37:21.560 --> 01:37:23.270
去他的全世界
Fuck the world.


748
01:37:24.890 --> 01:37:27.270
你很显然经历了很多
You've obviously been through a great deal.


749
01:37:28.520 --> 01:37:31.020
我完全无法想像
I can't begin to imagine what.


750
01:37:31.730 --> 01:37:35.110
但不管你发生什么事 现在都拥有超能力
But whatever happened to you, you have gifts now.


751
01:37:35.360 --> 01:37:37.070
超能力
Gifts?


752
01:37:37.240 --> 01:37:39.410
这看起来像是超能力吗
What part of this looks like a gift to you?


753
01:37:39.570 --> 01:37:40.740
我们需要你 维克多
We need you, Victor.


754
01:37:41.410 --> 01:37:43.000
也许你也需要我们
And maybe you need us.


755
01:37:43.160 --> 01:37:44.830
我不需要任何人
I don't need anyone.


756
01:37:47.040 --> 01:37:48.080
不再需要了
Not anymore.


757
01:37:48.250 --> 01:37:50.750
我以前也一直这么告诉自己
I told myself the same for a long time.


758
01:37:57.590 --> 01:38:00.300
我曾经失去一个深爱的人
I lost someone I loved once.


759
01:38:03.180 --> 01:38:07.980
把自己封闭起来
I shut myself off from everyone.


760
01:38:09.610 --> 01:38:12.320
但我得学会再次敞开心房
But I had to learn to open back up again.


761
01:38:15.030 --> 01:38:18.450
老实说 我仍在努力中
The truth is, I'm still working on it.


762
01:38:18.610 --> 01:38:21.830
既然你要求见我
And if you asked to meet me...


763
01:38:22.700 --> 01:38:25.450
你也在努力
you're working on it, too.


764
01:38:52.230 --> 01:38:57.570
挚爱的儿子
维克多·斯通 1994-2015


765
01:38:54.980 --> 01:38:57.570
挚爱的母亲
爱莲诺·斯通 1973-2015


766
01:39:37.150 --> 01:39:40.820
超人飞船上的金属样本被你说中了
You were right about the metal sample from the Superman ship.


767
01:39:40.990 --> 01:39:44.120
我们用电子激光向它轰射X光
When we bombard it with X-rays from the electron-laser,


768
01:39:44.530 --> 01:39:45.990
看看发生了什么事
look what happens.


769
01:39:55.000 --> 01:39:56.920
克氏350万度

770
01:39:57.090 --> 01:40:00.050
金属的内核变得过热
The inner core of the metal becomes superheated.


771
01:40:00.220 --> 01:40:02.550
形成又热又密的物质
Hot, dense matter.


772
01:40:05.850 --> 01:40:08.640
这是地球上最火热的东西
You're looking at the hottest thing on Earth.


773
01:40:08.810 --> 01:40:10.730
跟我对毕业舞会舞伴说的话一样
Exact words I said to my prom date.


774
01:40:11.100 --> 01:40:12.640
但她还是甩了我
She dumped me anyway.


775
01:40:13.100 --> 01:40:14.020
是啊
Yeah.


776
01:40:18.190 --> 01:40:19.030
喂 博士
Hey, Doc,


777
01:40:19.360 --> 01:40:23.820
你认为蝙蝠侠和犯罪调查部 找的东西有关联吗
do you think Batman is connected to the object the CID is looking for?


778
01:40:24.870 --> 01:40:27.990
6-1-9-8-2号物件
You know, 6-1-9-8-2?


779
01:40:29.160 --> 01:40:30.250
不
No...


780
01:40:31.250 --> 01:40:32.460
我不这么认为
I don't.


781
01:41:07.280 --> 01:41:09.370
维克多
Oh, Victor.


782
01:41:26.510 --> 01:41:28.430
好了 走吧
All right! Let's go!


783
01:41:29.760 --> 01:41:31.270
-高登局长 -来吧
Commissioner Gordon? Come on!


784
01:41:32.310 --> 01:41:33.230
给你的留言
Your messages.


785
01:41:37.940 --> 01:41:40.520
不用看也知道今天是满月
Don't have to see the sky to know it's a full moon.


786
01:41:40.690 --> 01:41:43.530
哥谭市一半的疯子都出来了
Half of Gotham's reality-challenged community showed up.


787
01:41:43.690 --> 01:41:45.860
他们都说看到怪物飞过港口
Say they saw flying monsters by the harbor.


788
01:41:46.030 --> 01:41:49.780
你是对的 老妈 金牌警校军 念牙医学院有什么不好
You were right, Ma. Police Academy. What's wrong with dental school?


789
01:41:52.870 --> 01:41:55.160
"遭到飞行吸血鬼攻击"
"Attacked by a flying vampire."


790
01:41:56.160 --> 01:41:59.130
"看起来像是一口尖牙的巨大蝙蝠"
"Looked like a giant bat with huge fangs."


791
01:41:59.290 --> 01:42:01.090
有一个相关的线索
On a possibly related note,


792
01:42:01.250 --> 01:42:04.840
实验室绑架案的嫌犯肖像素描
sketch of the suspect in the abductions at the lab across the harbor.


793
01:42:05.010 --> 01:42:07.550
-看起来像… -我知道像什么
-Looks like... -I know what it looks like, Crispus.


794
01:42:08.760 --> 01:42:11.220
拜托 你觉得他在这里打击犯罪20年
Come on, you think he fights criminals for 20 years here


795
01:42:11.390 --> 01:42:14.060
然后跑去大都会绑架八个人
and then he goes to Metropolis and kidnaps eight people?


796
01:42:15.100 --> 01:42:16.180
我今晚会找他谈谈
I'll talk to him tonight.


797
01:42:16.350 --> 01:42:17.890
怎么找他
How, Jim?


798
01:42:18.060 --> 01:42:19.520
你说呢
How do you think?


799
01:42:37.790 --> 01:42:39.000
塞拉斯
Silas?


800
01:42:46.760 --> 01:42:48.930
-天啊 -钢骨在哪里
-Oh, my goodness. -Where's the cyborg?


801
01:42:49.090 --> 01:42:50.260
他叫维克多
His name is Victor.


802
01:42:51.050 --> 01:42:53.810
我们见过面 说过话
We met, spoke.


803
01:42:54.770 --> 01:42:56.180
给他点时间
Give him time.


804
01:42:56.980 --> 01:42:58.940
你一定是巴里 我是戴安娜
You must be Barry. I'm Diana.


805
01:42:59.100 --> 01:43:02.860
你好 巴里 我是戴安娜 那不太对 好极了
Hi, Barry. I'm Diana. That's not right. Great.


806
01:43:03.020 --> 01:43:04.020
就只有我们
-So, this is us.


807
01:43:04.190 --> 01:43:05.150
没错 就只有我们
-Yeah, this is us.


808
01:43:06.490 --> 01:43:09.530
酷啊 那是蝙蝠信号 那是在…
Awesome! It's the Bat-Signal. That's your...


809
01:43:09.700 --> 01:43:11.780
抱歉 那是在呼叫你
Oh, sorry. That's your signal.


810
01:43:11.950 --> 01:43:13.160
意思是我们得出动了
That means we have to go now.


811
01:43:13.330 --> 01:43:16.370
-对 是这意思没错 -酷毙了
-Yeah, that's what that means. -It's so cool.


812
01:44:14.470 --> 01:44:17.930
湄拉指挥官 我告诉海王 外围守卫被掳走
Commander Mera, I told the king the perimeter guards were taken.


813
01:44:18.140 --> 01:44:19.680
他不会派出援兵
He won't send reinforcements.


814
01:44:19.850 --> 01:44:22.480
他说所有的士兵 都必须前往叛军地区支持
He says all the reserves are needed in the rebel regions.


815
01:44:22.640 --> 01:44:25.360
他不但残忍而且短视
He's as shortsighted as he is cruel.


816
01:44:27.070 --> 01:44:28.650
好吧 带着剩下的人马
All right, take what men we have left


817
01:44:28.820 --> 01:44:30.990
在母盒周围形成方阵
and form a phalanx around the Mother Box.


818
01:46:10.420 --> 01:46:12.460
你逃不了的
You can't escape.


819
01:46:13.210 --> 01:46:15.170
我并不想逃
I'm not trying to.


820
01:48:17.750 --> 01:48:19.630
维科跟我说你会来
Vulko told me you would come.


821
01:48:20.130 --> 01:48:22.840
备受爱戴的亚特兰娜女王的长子
The firstborn of beloved Queen Atlanna.


822
01:48:25.470 --> 01:48:26.760
等一下
Wait.


823
01:48:28.770 --> 01:48:29.850
拜托了
Please.


824
01:48:33.440 --> 01:48:34.770
我认识她
I knew her.


825
01:48:37.070 --> 01:48:38.650
你至少认识她
Well, that makes one of us.


826
01:48:39.530 --> 01:48:41.110
我父母死于战争
My parents died in the wars.


827
01:48:43.030 --> 01:48:44.240
她收容了我
She took me in.


828
01:48:44.620 --> 01:48:45.870
还真是个圣人
What a saint.


829
01:48:46.580 --> 01:48:48.700
你胆敢讽刺亚特兰娜女王
You dare speak of Queen Atlanna that way?


830
01:48:48.870 --> 01:48:51.500
你的女王把我丢在我父亲家门口
Your queen left me on my father's doorstep


831
01:48:51.660 --> 01:48:53.250
从此把我忘得一干二净
and never gave me another thought.


832
01:48:53.420 --> 01:48:55.630
你母亲是为了救你才离开
Your mother left you to save your life.


833
01:48:56.750 --> 01:48:59.210
你无法想像她有多心痛
You cannot imagine how it hurt her.


834
01:49:00.800 --> 01:49:02.840
她也付出惨痛代价
What it cost her.


835
01:49:04.090 --> 01:49:06.260
但你现在不是脆弱的小孩
But you're not a defenseless child now.


836
01:49:08.680 --> 01:49:10.270
那本是她的责任
It would have been her responsibility


837
01:49:10.430 --> 01:49:13.600
跟着那怪物到陆地 然后阻止他
to follow that monster to the surface and stop him.


838
01:49:14.190 --> 01:49:15.270
现在
Now,


839
01:49:16.560 --> 01:49:17.900
是你的责任
it's yours.


840
01:50:22.250 --> 01:50:23.710
太好了
Yes.


841
01:50:46.650 --> 01:50:48.030
荒原狼
Steppenwolf,


842
01:50:48.200 --> 01:50:50.120
告诉我你知道了什么
tell me what you've learned.


843
01:50:50.280 --> 01:50:52.910
找到两个苏醒的母盒
Two boxes found and awake.


844
01:50:53.080 --> 01:50:56.040
结合两个母盒的力量
With the combined power of the two Mother Boxes,


845
01:50:56.200 --> 01:50:59.210
我完成了要塞的防御系统
I've been able to finish the stronghold's defenses.


846
01:50:59.370 --> 01:51:01.790
第三个母盒在哪里
Where is the third Mother Box?


847
01:51:01.960 --> 01:51:06.090
天启魔感应到它 正在寻找它
The parademons sense its presence and search for the third.


848
01:51:06.260 --> 01:51:07.260
它们抓来了囚犯
They have taken prisoners


849
01:51:07.420 --> 01:51:09.510
他们带有它的气味
who carry its scent.


850
01:51:10.260 --> 01:51:11.300
去吧
Go.


851
01:51:12.140 --> 01:51:14.060
去审问囚犯
Interrogate the prisoners.


852
01:51:14.850 --> 01:51:16.730
找到第三个母盒
Find the third.


853
01:51:18.270 --> 01:51:20.440
他们会乖乖告诉我
They will tell me what they know,


854
01:51:21.690 --> 01:51:24.190
不然我就来硬的
or I will rip it from them.


855
01:51:29.860 --> 01:51:35.080
第四章

856
01:51:31.460 --> 01:51:35.080
“改造机器”

857
01:52:07.530 --> 01:52:09.110
你们有多少人
How many of you are there?


858
01:52:09.950 --> 01:52:11.070
还不够多
Not enough.


859
01:52:13.160 --> 01:52:15.410
哥谭市各地有数十名目击者
Dozens of witnesses all over Gotham.


860
01:52:15.580 --> 01:52:18.290
他们的描述符合大都会绑架案的嫌犯
Description matches the suspect in the Metropolis abductions.


861
01:52:18.870 --> 01:52:19.910
天启魔
Parademons.


862
01:52:20.540 --> 01:52:21.790
好吧
Okay.


863
01:52:21.960 --> 01:52:24.290
天启魔一定闻到母盒的气味
The demons must have caught the scent of a Mother Box.


864
01:52:24.540 --> 01:52:25.540
在实验室的那个
At the lab.


865
01:52:25.710 --> 01:52:28.050
它们把人抓走 拷问母盒下落
They carried people away to find out what they know.


866
01:52:28.210 --> 01:52:29.920
-那八个人可能还活着 -九个人
So the eight may still be alive. Nine.


867
01:52:32.470 --> 01:52:34.970
星辰实验室的主任今晚被绑走
The head of STARLABS was taken tonight.


868
01:52:40.180 --> 01:52:42.730
好吧 另一个科学家
Wow, okay. So, another scientist.


869
01:52:42.890 --> 01:52:44.190
我们要怎么找到他
So, how do we find him?


870
01:52:44.350 --> 01:52:46.020
附近一定有它们的巢穴
There must be a nest nearby.


871
01:52:46.190 --> 01:52:50.280
我在大都会和哥谭市地图上做记号
I plotted all the sightings in Metropolis, Gotham.


872
01:52:50.440 --> 01:52:52.570
看不出任何模式
No discernable pattern I can see.


873
01:52:52.740 --> 01:52:54.030
地图上的路线没有交集
The lines on the map don't converge.


874
01:52:54.200 --> 01:52:55.530
在陆地上没有
On land.


875
01:52:56.240 --> 01:52:58.290
这是在两座城市之间的史崔克岛
These lead back to Stryker's Island, between the two cities.


876
01:52:58.450 --> 01:53:00.870
这些是通风口 全都通往1929年
These are air vents. They all lead down to the tunnel


877
01:53:01.040 --> 01:53:03.420
废弃的大都会工程隧道
to a Metropolis project that was abandoned in '29.


878
01:53:03.580 --> 01:53:05.170
巢穴可能在那里
The nest could be there.


879
01:53:06.500 --> 01:53:07.880
他要跟我们一起去吗
Uh, is he coming with us now,


880
01:53:08.050 --> 01:53:09.380
因为你的车子坐不下
because we're not all gonna fit in your car.


881
01:53:09.920 --> 01:53:11.340
我有更大的玩意儿
I have something bigger.


882
01:53:12.670 --> 01:53:14.300
你真的觉得…
Do you really think that...


883
01:53:15.640 --> 01:53:19.180
他们就这样闪人了吗
Oh, wow, they just... They really just vanish, huh?


884
01:53:20.390 --> 01:53:21.730
太没礼貌了
Oh. That's rude.


885
01:53:56.760 --> 01:54:00.260
星辰实验室

886
01:54:00.430 --> 01:54:02.520
很接近了
We're close.


887
01:54:02.680 --> 01:54:04.690
敌人的气味
The scent of the enemy.


888
01:54:05.390 --> 01:54:06.560
虚无
Of absence.


889
01:54:07.150 --> 01:54:08.690
黑暗
Darkness.


890
01:54:09.440 --> 01:54:10.400
死亡
Death.


891
01:54:10.820 --> 01:54:13.070
-我们在哪里 阿尔弗雷德 -史崔克岛
Where are we, Alfred? Stryker's Island.


892
01:54:13.240 --> 01:54:17.780
你们应该就在隧道通风塔的正下方
You should be directly under the venting tower for the tunnel.


893
01:54:18.370 --> 01:54:21.790
往左看 应该有一道阶梯通往机械室
Now look to your left, you'll see a staircase to the machine room.


894
01:54:21.990 --> 01:54:24.540
红外线热影像显示有一群人
Thermal scan shows a cluster of people there.


895
01:54:24.710 --> 01:54:25.620
就是那里
That's it.


896
01:54:26.000 --> 01:54:27.000
走吧
Let's go.


897
01:54:41.010 --> 01:54:41.850
好吧
Right.


898
01:54:42.060 --> 01:54:43.930
有任何计划吗
Is there... Is there a plan?


899
01:54:45.480 --> 01:54:46.770
你们两个
Either of you?


900
01:54:46.940 --> 01:54:48.100
别单打独斗
Don't engage alone.


901
01:54:48.900 --> 01:54:50.150
我们要联手出击
We do this together.


902
01:54:59.110 --> 01:55:00.950
我听说过你
I heard about you.


903
01:55:02.740 --> 01:55:03.910
没想到你是真的
Didn't think you were real.


904
01:55:04.370 --> 01:55:05.910
有用的时候我就是真的
I'm real when it's useful.


905
01:55:16.170 --> 01:55:20.300
我受够了你们的沉默 快告诉我 母盒在哪里
I grow tired of your silence. Now tell me, where is the Mother Box?


906
01:55:27.100 --> 01:55:29.310
求求你 我们有家人
Please. We have families.


907
01:55:29.480 --> 01:55:31.560
那你们就有弱点
Then you have weakness.


908
01:55:31.730 --> 01:55:33.190
荒原狼
Steppenwolf.


909
01:55:33.360 --> 01:55:37.530
好吧 我猜…那就是坏蛋
Okay, I'm guessing that's the bad guy.


910
01:55:37.690 --> 01:55:38.740
猜对了
Good guess.


911
01:55:39.280 --> 01:55:42.740
我现在真的超想念超人
I'm really, really missing Superman right now.


912
01:55:42.910 --> 01:55:45.080
绕到另一边
Circle to the other side.


913
01:55:45.240 --> 01:55:47.250
把它们团团围住展开突袭
We'll surround them and surprise him.


914
01:55:51.790 --> 01:55:53.380
你接近过一个母盒
You have been near a Mother Box.


915
01:55:53.840 --> 01:55:55.550
身上有它的气味
The scent is on you.


916
01:55:55.710 --> 01:55:57.170
我不知道你在说什么
I don't know what you're talking about.


917
01:55:57.340 --> 01:55:59.170
-它在哪里 -放过他
-Where is it? -Leave him alone!


918
01:55:59.340 --> 01:56:01.590
他不知道
He... He doesn't know.


919
01:56:05.180 --> 01:56:06.970
等等 求求你
Wait, please, please!


920
01:56:12.150 --> 01:56:15.270
你也带着气味 但是更强烈
You carry the scent, too. But stronger.


921
01:56:15.650 --> 01:56:17.780
我死也不会告诉你
I will die before I tell you.


922
01:56:17.940 --> 01:56:19.780
不告诉我就会死
You'll die if you don't.


923
01:56:20.200 --> 01:56:21.200
不
No!


924
01:56:30.540 --> 01:56:31.580
维克多
Victor.


925
01:56:31.750 --> 01:56:33.040
杀了他们
Kill them both.


926
01:56:37.500 --> 01:56:38.670
亚马逊女战士
Ah, Amazon.


927
01:56:39.090 --> 01:56:41.590
但不像你的姐妹
But not like your sisters.


928
01:56:41.760 --> 01:56:43.010
你更强大
Stronger.


929
01:57:13.960 --> 01:57:15.580
亚马逊女战士
Amazon.


930
01:57:18.630 --> 01:57:20.010
住手
Hold!


931
01:57:20.380 --> 01:57:22.590
这一个是我的
This one will be mine.


932
01:57:24.550 --> 01:57:26.970
我不属于任何人
I belong to no one.


933
01:57:40.980 --> 01:57:43.030
大伙儿 这不是联手出击
Guys, this is not together.


934
01:57:50.040 --> 01:57:51.200
把这些人救出去
Help get those people out of here.


935
01:57:51.370 --> 01:57:53.040
我会让这些怪物跟着我
I'll make sure these things follow me.


936
01:58:03.470 --> 01:58:04.880
大伙儿 快啊
Everybody, move!


937
01:58:13.640 --> 01:58:15.140
再快一点
A little quicker.


938
01:58:17.520 --> 01:58:18.900
-没事吧 -没事
-Are you good? -Yeah.


939
01:58:19.060 --> 01:58:21.480
我会搞定 动作快点
I've got this. Keep moving.


940
01:58:23.530 --> 01:58:24.530
这里
This way.


941
01:59:00.860 --> 01:59:02.270
能量正在消散
The energy is dissipating.


942
01:59:02.440 --> 01:59:03.940
我的手套很有用
My gauntlet worked!


943
01:59:05.190 --> 01:59:07.490
晚点再庆祝 阿尔弗雷德 我需要夜蝠战机
Celebrate later, Alfred. I need the Nightcrawler.


944
01:59:07.650 --> 01:59:09.280
我以为你不会开口
Thought you'd never ask.


945
01:59:09.870 --> 01:59:11.990
马上赶去 启动遥控模式
Crawler's on the way. Initiating remote mode.


946
01:59:42.150 --> 01:59:43.150
谢了 阿尔弗雷德
Thank you, Alfred.


947
01:59:43.320 --> 01:59:44.730
不客气
Don't mention it.


948
02:00:07.460 --> 02:00:08.420
惨了
No!


949
02:00:16.430 --> 02:00:17.890
他们安全了 回去隧道
They're safe. Get back to the tunnel.


950
02:00:18.060 --> 02:00:21.140
隧道 好 外星人 坏蛋 耍剑的女士
Tunnel. Right. Aliens, bad guy, sword lady.


951
02:00:32.950 --> 02:00:34.320
轮到我
My turn.


952
02:01:56.700 --> 02:01:58.200
系统全面故障
Catastrophic failure of all systems.


953
02:01:58.370 --> 02:02:00.790
你没事吧 韦恩少爷
Are you all right, Master Wayne?


954
02:02:00.950 --> 02:02:01.950
你没事吧
Are you all right?


955
02:02:12.670 --> 02:02:16.180
你身上流着旧神族的血液
You have the blood of the old gods in you.


956
02:02:30.650 --> 02:02:31.480
你没事吧
You okay?


957
02:02:33.490 --> 02:02:35.110
我不确定你会来
Wasn't sure you'd come.


958
02:02:36.150 --> 02:02:37.450
你是我父亲
You're my father.


959
02:02:40.950 --> 02:02:41.950
快去吧
Go.


960
02:02:55.590 --> 02:02:56.590
不要
No!


961
02:03:42.100 --> 02:03:44.430
放轻松 阿尔弗雷德 我来接手
Relax, Alfred. I'll take it from here.


962
02:03:46.640 --> 02:03:47.850
我认识你吗
Uh, do I know you?


963
02:04:18.760 --> 02:04:20.010
我们在哪里的下面
What are we under, right now?


964
02:04:20.760 --> 02:04:22.050
哥谭港
Gotham Harbor.


965
02:05:00.760 --> 02:05:02.050
那是谁
Who is that?


966
02:05:27.370 --> 02:05:28.540
快点
Come on.


967
02:05:33.670 --> 02:05:34.880
戴安娜 快上来
Diana, get on!


968
02:06:36.770 --> 02:06:38.270
是什么
What is it?


969
02:06:46.070 --> 02:06:47.490
让我看
Show me.


970
02:07:26.650 --> 02:07:28.280
它在这里
It is here.


971
02:07:29.030 --> 02:07:31.990
在这个世界
On this world.


972
02:08:05.900 --> 02:08:08.860
你可能感染了外星微生物 必须接受隔离
Sir, you're gonna be in quarantine for possible alien microbes.


973
02:08:09.030 --> 02:08:10.700
美国政府的规定要求…
U.S. government protocols require that...


974
02:08:10.860 --> 02:08:13.660
我知道规定 是我写的
I know the requirements. I wrote them.


975
02:08:18.210 --> 02:08:19.540
它召唤了他
It called to him.


976
02:08:19.710 --> 02:08:21.250
母盒
The Mother Box.


977
02:08:21.420 --> 02:08:22.790
他抢走的那个
The one he already has.


978
02:08:23.130 --> 02:08:26.170
他有两个了 他从亚特兰蒂斯抢走母盒
He has two. He took the Mother Box from Atlantis.


979
02:08:26.340 --> 02:08:28.630
现在只需要人类遗失的母盒
All he needs now is the lost Box of Men.


980
02:08:28.800 --> 02:08:29.970
他可能已经拿到手了
If he doesn't already have it.


981
02:08:33.640 --> 02:08:35.060
他没有拿到手
He doesn't have it.


982
02:08:38.270 --> 02:08:39.430
在我这里
I do.


983
02:08:49.990 --> 02:08:52.070
你完成征服行动了吗
Have you finished the conquest?


984
02:08:52.240 --> 02:08:53.490
还没有 狄萨德
Not yet, DeSaad.


985
02:08:53.660 --> 02:08:55.910
那你为何召唤我
Then why do you summon me?


986
02:08:56.080 --> 02:08:57.740
我带来消息
I bring news.


987
02:08:57.910 --> 02:09:00.830
强大的达克赛德登上王位之前
Before mighty Darkseid came to the throne,


988
02:09:01.000 --> 02:09:05.500
他在全宇宙搜寻终极武器
he searched the universe for the ultimate weapon.


989
02:09:06.130 --> 02:09:08.300
反生命方程序
The Anti-Life Equation.


990
02:09:08.460 --> 02:09:13.140
掌控多重宇宙中 所有生命与自由意志的关键
The key to controlling all life and all will throughout the multiverse.


991
02:09:13.300 --> 02:09:16.310
他发现它被藏在一个原始星球上 但在他还没…
He found it hidden on a primitive planet, but before...


992
02:09:16.470 --> 02:09:19.350
大家都知道你背叛了他
The story of the defiance is well-known.


993
02:09:19.520 --> 02:09:22.020
我找到了那个原始星球
I have found the primitive planet.


994
02:09:22.190 --> 02:09:24.230
胆敢反击的世界
The world that fought back.


995
02:09:24.400 --> 02:09:26.270
就是地球
It is Earth.


996
02:09:26.440 --> 02:09:28.650
反生命方程序被刻在…
The Anti-Life Equation is carved


997
02:09:28.820 --> 02:09:32.700
这个世界的地表
into the surface of this very world.


998
02:09:36.370 --> 02:09:37.780
你确定
Are you certain?


999
02:09:37.950 --> 02:09:38.990
我看到了
I have seen it.


1000
02:09:39.160 --> 02:09:42.580
我亲眼看到了
I have looked with my own eyes.


1001
02:10:25.920 --> 02:10:27.500
主人
My lord.


1002
02:10:29.040 --> 02:10:32.590
荒原狼
Oh, Steppenwolf.


1003
02:10:33.260 --> 02:10:36.340
主人 我只是你谦卑的仆人
My lord, I am but your humble servant.


1004
02:10:37.340 --> 02:10:40.180
你真的找到它了
Can it be true that you have found it?


1005
02:10:40.350 --> 02:10:42.520
是的 霸主
I have, great one.


1006
02:10:43.270 --> 02:10:46.230
失落的世界就是地球
The lost world is Earth.


1007
02:10:46.400 --> 02:10:49.400
反生命方程序就在这里
Anti-Life is here.


1008
02:10:50.730 --> 02:10:54.070
你若想寻求救赎 那就找到第三个母盒
If it is redemption you seek, find the third box,


1009
02:10:54.240 --> 02:10:57.200
合而为一形成三位一体 当这世界化为焦土
synchronize The Unity, and when this world is scorched,


1010
02:10:57.360 --> 02:11:00.580
我就会来拿我的大奖
I will come for my great prize.


1011
02:11:01.540 --> 02:11:03.750
你会来地球
You will come to Earth?


1012
02:11:04.790 --> 02:11:09.040
我已经把十万个世界化为尘土
I have turned 100,000 worlds to dust


1013
02:11:09.210 --> 02:11:10.710
寻找反生命方程序
looking for Anti-Life.


1014
02:11:10.880 --> 02:11:14.090
寻找抢走我荣耀之人
Looking for those who robbed me of my glory.


1015
02:11:14.260 --> 02:11:20.010
我将踏着他们的骨骸 沐浴在反生命方程序的荣光中
I will stride across their bones and bask in the glow of Anti-Life.


1016
02:11:20.180 --> 02:11:22.890
所有的生命
And all of existence


1017
02:11:23.060 --> 02:11:26.560
都将是我的
shall be mine.


1018
02:11:29.940 --> 02:11:33.860
一定会的 主人
It shall be so, my master.


1019
02:11:38.070 --> 02:11:39.740
酷爆了
So cool.


1020
02:11:39.910 --> 02:11:42.450
从外面看 这只是一栋废弃建筑物
From the outside, it looks like this building was abandoned.


1021
02:11:46.200 --> 02:11:47.960
它想要飞行
It wants to fly.


1022
02:11:49.170 --> 02:11:51.040
你和机器说话
You talk to machines?


1023
02:11:51.340 --> 02:11:53.340
我和人工智能说话
I speak to intelligence.


1024
02:11:53.500 --> 02:11:56.380
这个说她因为软体问题不能飞
This one's saying she can't fly because of a software issue,


1025
02:11:56.550 --> 02:11:58.510
不过我很快就能修好
but I could fix it with a little time.


1026
02:12:08.270 --> 02:12:10.480
我的数据流中有个黑点
There's a dark spot in my data stream.


1027
02:12:10.810 --> 02:12:13.070
我能感应到另外两个母盒
I could feel the other two boxes.


1028
02:12:13.230 --> 02:12:15.070
我知道它们苏醒了
I know they're awake,


1029
02:12:15.230 --> 02:12:16.740
但是看不见它们在哪里
but I can't see where they are.


1030
02:12:16.900 --> 02:12:18.900
知道敌方基地在哪里才能攻击
Well, we can't attack unless we know where the base is.


1031
02:12:19.070 --> 02:12:21.320
就算我们知道
Even if we knew,


1032
02:12:21.490 --> 02:12:24.330
也没有比荒原狼更强大的生物
I've never seen a being as strong as Steppenwolf.


1033
02:12:26.540 --> 02:12:27.910
也许有一个
Maybe one.


1034
02:12:28.290 --> 02:12:29.670
超人
Hmm, Superman.


1035
02:12:30.580 --> 02:12:34.630
只要第三个母盒在沉睡 他们就看不到它 只能感应到它
As long as the third box is asleep, they can't see it, only sense it.


1036
02:12:34.800 --> 02:12:36.840
我们得不断移动才不会被发现
We need to keep moving so they can't catch up.


1037
02:12:37.010 --> 02:12:40.180
不 这只是延缓失败的策略 不是获胜的战略
No. That's just a strategy to lose more slowly, not to win.


1038
02:12:40.800 --> 02:12:42.800
难道火焰喷射器不流行了吗
Remind me, are flamethrowers not a thing?


1039
02:12:43.680 --> 02:12:44.760
为何不直接烧毁它
Why don't we just destroy it?


1040
02:12:44.930 --> 02:12:47.020
烈火也无法摧毁母盒
Fire doesn't destroy the boxes.


1041
02:12:47.180 --> 02:12:48.930
它们是一种未知的物质
They're an unknown form of matter.


1042
02:12:49.100 --> 02:12:52.560
喜欢热能 会吸收它 保存在它们的核心
Oh, they love heat. They absorb it, hold it in their cores.


1043
02:12:52.730 --> 02:12:54.860
你很了解这些盒子嘛
Well, you know a lot about these boxes.


1044
02:12:55.440 --> 02:12:56.690
非常可疑
Makes you think.


1045
02:12:56.860 --> 02:12:58.570
你在哪里找到母盒
Where'd you find the box, Victor?


1046
02:12:59.530 --> 02:13:00.950
你在怀疑我吗
Are you trying to say something?


1047
02:13:01.240 --> 02:13:02.740
我就是怀疑你
Oh, I'm saying it.


1048
02:13:03.320 --> 02:13:05.200
我们怎么知道你不是他们的奸细
How do we know you're not working for them?


1049
02:13:07.080 --> 02:13:08.750
说来话长
It's a long story.


1050
02:13:09.200 --> 02:13:11.120
你赶着要去哪儿吗
You got somewhere else to be?


1051
02:13:18.510 --> 02:13:22.340
纳粹在二战结束前找到母盒
The Nazis found the box at the end of the Second World War,


1052
02:13:22.510 --> 02:13:25.550
它被埋在一座义大利修道院底下
buried under an Italian monastery.


1053
02:13:25.720 --> 02:13:28.100
被送去给希特勒的路上 遭到盟军拦截
The Allies intercepted it on its way to Hitler.


1054
02:13:28.270 --> 02:13:30.480
1944年被带回了美国
They brought it back to the States in '44.


1055
02:13:31.060 --> 02:13:34.610
6-1-9-8-2号未知物件
Unknown object 6-1-9-8-2.


1056
02:13:35.480 --> 02:13:38.940
它被丢在五角大厦档案室七十年
It collected dust in the Pentagon archives for 70 years


1057
02:13:39.480 --> 02:13:42.700
直到国防部开始研究超人飞船
till DoD began to study the Superman ship.


1058
02:13:44.240 --> 02:13:47.740
星辰实验室的一位研究员 发现超人飞船和…
A researcher at STARLABS made a connection between the ship...


1059
02:13:49.040 --> 02:13:50.580
6-1-9-8-2号物件有关联
and 6-1-9-8-2.


1060
02:13:51.460 --> 02:13:54.290
他了解到它们都是外星科技
He understood they were both alien technologies.


1061
02:13:54.960 --> 02:13:56.540
不同的文明
Different civilizations,


1062
02:13:57.130 --> 02:13:59.250
类似的属性
similar properties.


1063
02:14:00.590 --> 02:14:03.340
虽然母盒已经沉睡了几千年
And though the box had slept for thousands of years,


1064
02:14:04.010 --> 02:14:06.850
那位研究员想出 一个可以唤醒它的理论
the researcher formulated a theory on how to awaken it.


1065
02:14:07.470 --> 02:14:09.220
也真的唤醒了它
And so did.


1066
02:14:11.680 --> 02:14:12.520
后来…
Then...


1067
02:14:14.650 --> 02:14:16.560
我出了车祸 本来应该死去
I had an accident that should've killed me.


1068
02:14:17.900 --> 02:14:21.110
但是出于绝望或是疯狂
But in an act of desperation or madness,


1069
02:14:21.280 --> 02:14:23.610
那位研究员驾驭了母盒的力量
the researcher harnessed the power of the Mother Box.


1070
02:14:39.800 --> 02:14:41.880
释放了一种他无法…
He unleashed an alien technology


1071
02:14:42.050 --> 02:14:44.720
完全理解的外星科技
he didn't fully understand.


1072
02:14:44.880 --> 02:14:47.260
他利用那股力量让我活下来
He used that power to keep me alive.


1073
02:14:50.850 --> 02:14:52.430
活着…
Alive...


1074
02:14:52.980 --> 02:14:54.940
但变成了这样
but turned into this.


1075
02:14:57.730 --> 02:15:00.020
母盒继续沉睡
The box went back to sleep


1076
02:15:00.940 --> 02:15:02.610
他也没有物归原处
and he never returned it.


1077
02:15:05.240 --> 02:15:07.280
那位研究员就是塞拉斯·斯通
That researcher was Silas Stone.


1078
02:15:08.990 --> 02:15:10.660
我的父亲
My father.


1079
02:15:13.950 --> 02:15:15.620
等等
Wait,


1080
02:15:15.790 --> 02:15:19.170
你父亲用一个母盒救了你一命
your father saved your life with one of these things?


1081
02:15:19.330 --> 02:15:21.550
它们不是变态杀人机器吗
Aren't they psycho murder machines?


1082
02:15:21.710 --> 02:15:24.090
它们是改造机器
They're change machines.


1083
02:15:24.260 --> 02:15:26.930
母盒没有救人或杀人…
The boxes don't think in terms of healing or killing,


1084
02:15:27.340 --> 02:15:29.430
活着或死亡的概念
alive or dead.


1085
02:15:29.590 --> 02:15:31.850
它们按照主人的意愿重新排列物质
They rearrange matter at the will of their masters,


1086
02:15:32.010 --> 02:15:33.600
使其再生 恢复原状
regenerate, reinstate.


1087
02:15:33.770 --> 02:15:35.180
恢复原状
Reinstate?


1088
02:15:35.350 --> 02:15:38.770
母盒拥有恢复粒子相互作用的力量
A box has the power to reinstate anterior particle relationships.


1089
02:15:38.940 --> 02:15:42.020
你是说任何物质的粒子 都不能被创造或毁灭
So, you mean in the way that particles of matter can't be created or destroyed,


1090
02:15:42.190 --> 02:15:44.190
它们的相互作用只会转变
their relations just transform.


1091
02:15:44.360 --> 02:15:47.110
烧掉一栋房子 粒子仍然存在
Burn down a house, the particles still exist.


1092
02:15:47.280 --> 02:15:49.740
房子的粒子变成灰烬的粒子
Particles of house become particles of smoke.


1093
02:15:49.910 --> 02:15:53.950
任何人只要有火柴 都能把一栋房子化成灰烬
Anybody with a match can turn a house to smoke.


1094
02:15:56.000 --> 02:15:57.750
但是一个母盒
But a Mother Box...


1095
02:15:57.910 --> 02:16:00.130
能够把灰烬变回一栋房子
...turns smoke back into a house.


1096
02:16:06.130 --> 02:16:08.630
我知道我们都在想同样的事
I know we're all thinking the same thing right now.


1097
02:16:10.090 --> 02:16:12.600
谁要说我才不说
Who's gonna say it? I'm not gonna say it.


1098
02:16:39.870 --> 02:16:40.960
谁啊
Who is it?


1099
02:16:41.670 --> 02:16:42.880
玛莎
Martha.


1100
