1106
02:17:27.960 --> 02:17:29.920
只要你需要的话
for as long as you need.


1107
02:17:31.130 --> 02:17:33.760
谢谢你 露易丝 你真好心
Thank you, Lois. That's very kind.


1108
02:17:35.430 --> 02:17:37.510
但我找到一个小地方 我一个人住刚好
But I've found a little place that suits me just fine,


1109
02:17:37.680 --> 02:17:39.140
就在餐馆旁边
right by the diner.


1110
02:17:39.770 --> 02:17:41.140
我不是来求助的
I'm not here for help.


1111
02:17:42.310 --> 02:17:44.190
我来是因为…
I'm here because


1112
02:17:45.020 --> 02:17:47.440
我见到派瑞先生 他跟我说…
when I saw Mr. Perry, he told me that


1113
