1124
02:18:34.400 --> 02:18:36.910
只有你知道
You're the only one who knows.


1125
02:18:37.070 --> 02:18:39.490
也只有你能体会
Who feels what I do.


1126
02:18:40.830 --> 02:18:43.790
悲伤加上秘密的负担
Burdened by a secret on top of grief.


1127
02:18:46.960 --> 02:18:50.250
我大老远跑来是因为我想…
I came all this way because I wanted...


1128
02:18:50.420 --> 02:18:52.420
因为我想来见你
because I wanted to see you.


1129
02:18:53.670 --> 02:18:55.630
告诉你
Tell you...


1130
02:18:55.800 --> 02:18:57.640
我能体会
