1133
02:19:09.230 --> 02:19:11.230
我也很想念他
And I just miss him.


1134
02:19:12.400 --> 02:19:14.610
我好想他啊
I miss him so much.


1135
02:19:21.330 --> 02:19:23.000
我也是 亲爱的
So do I, sweetheart.


1136
02:19:27.580 --> 02:19:32.460
玛莎 你有任何需要我都会帮忙
Martha, you know if there's anything you need, I'm here.


1137
02:19:36.050 --> 02:19:38.640
