1165
02:21:29.080 --> 02:21:31.500
直到超人死后
Not until Superman died.


1166
02:21:31.670 --> 02:21:34.210
-因为他们怕他 -没错
It's like they were afraid of him? Yes,


1167
02:21:34.790 --> 02:21:36.590
他们怕他
they were afraid of him.


1168
02:21:39.510 --> 02:21:41.300
这是唯一的办法
This is the only way.


1169
02:21:42.970 --> 02:21:46.720
这团队有六个人 不是五个人 没有他就没有我们
There are six, not five. There is no us without him.


