我父亲告诉我亚特兰蒂斯有句老话
You know, my father told me there's a saying in Atlantis...


1188
02:23:07.590 --> 02:23:09.890
"只要从黑暗中拿回什么
"None are taken back from the darkness.


1189
02:23:10.060 --> 02:23:12.680
"-就一定要… -就一定要付出代价"
"Not without...Not without giving one up in return."


