your guilt's overcome your reason.


1216
02:24:37.680 --> 02:24:39.810
再多的国王人马都办不到
Not all the king's horses nor all the king's men...


1217
02:24:39.980 --> 02:24:43.070
阿尔弗雷德 我这次完全凭靠信念
Alfred, for once, I'm operating strictly on faith,


1218
02:24:43.230 --> 02:24:45.070
而不是理性
not on reason.


1219
02:24:45.860 --> 02:24:50.070
但如果你开始玩弄这个母盒
