-Alfred. -Good day, ma'am.


1469
02:56:05.070 --> 02:56:06.950
这里真的很酷 阿尔弗雷德
It's badass, Alfred.


1470
02:56:09.740 --> 02:56:12.160
我去泡茶
Well, I'll put on the tea.


1471
02:56:12.330 --> 02:56:13.330
太好了
Great.


1472
02:56:13.500 --> 02:56:15.330
不知道哪里有这么多杯子
I don't know where we're gonna find the cups.


1473
02:56:18.250 --> 02:56:21.090
那就是母盒 就在那里
There's the Mother Box, right there.


1474
02:56:21.250 --> 02:56:23.050
显示可见光谱
Go to visible spectrum.


1475
02:56:25.930 --> 02:56:26.760
普扎诺夫
Pozharnov.


1476
02:56:27.340 --> 02:56:30.180
离莫斯科不远的鬼城
Ghost city not far from Moscow.


1477
02:56:30.350 --> 02:56:33.020
三十年前发生核事故后被废弃
It's been abandoned since the nuclear accident there 30 years ago.


1478
02:56:33.180 --> 02:56:34.390
就连军队也不进去
Not even the army goes in.


1479
02:56:34.560 --> 02:56:35.850
是啊 辐射性一定强到
Right, it's probably so radioactive


1480
02:56:36.020 --> 02:56:38.190
你的脖子会长出另一只脚
that you grow an extra foot outta your neck.


1481
02:56:38.360 --> 02:56:39.190
不再是这样了
Not anymore.


1482
02:56:39.360 --> 02:56:41.530
他收集了辐射 用来创建他的基地
He's harvested the radiation to build his base.


1483
02:56:41.690 --> 02:56:42.530
放大
Zoom.


1484
02:56:46.530 --> 02:56:47.910
他到底在盖什么
What the hell is he building?


1485
02:56:48.070 --> 02:56:49.320
三位一体在里面
The Unity's in there.


1486
02:56:49.490 --> 02:56:50.910
我们要从上面进攻
We'll attack from above.


1487
02:56:51.080 --> 02:56:53.660
炸药无法分开母盒
Explosives won't separate the boxes,


1488
02:56:53.830 --> 02:56:55.660
只会强化它们的联系
only strengthen their bond.


1489
02:56:55.830 --> 02:56:56.960
什么 我们不能炸掉它
What? So we can't blow it up?


1490
02:56:57.120 --> 02:56:58.580
不能从外面
Not from the outside.


1491
02:57:00.170 --> 02:57:02.550
我想插入合而为一的母盒
I want to plug into The Unity, one-on-one.


1492
02:57:03.260 --> 02:57:04.670
和它融为一体
Fuse with it.


1493
02:57:04.840 --> 02:57:07.380
从内部削弱它的连结 就能够再把它拆成三个
Weaken its bond from the inside so we can break it back into three.


1494
02:57:07.550 --> 02:57:09.760
不行 你不知道你会面对什么
No, you don't know what you'd be up against.


1495
02:57:09.930 --> 02:57:13.470
你得一个人融入三位一体
You'd have to stream into The Unity by yourself.


1496
02:57:13.640 --> 02:57:15.980
这三个母盒结合起来足以毁天灭地
These boxes together are world destroyers.


1497
02:57:16.140 --> 02:57:17.560
它们存在了十亿年
A billion years old.


1498
02:57:17.730 --> 02:57:19.860
绝对会钻进你脑袋 找到你的弱点
They'll get inside you and find your weaknesses


1499
02:57:20.020 --> 02:57:22.190
和你的恐惧 并用来摧毁你
and your fears, and use them to destroy you.


1500
02:57:22.360 --> 02:57:24.360
只要让我进去 替我争取时间
Just get me in and get me time.


1501
02:57:24.610 --> 02:57:25.780
你可能会死 维克多
You could die, Victor.


1502
02:57:25.940 --> 02:57:28.240
我不这样做 我们都会死
If I don't, we all die. Period.


1503
02:57:32.990 --> 02:57:34.750
我失去了一切
I got nothing left.


1504
02:57:40.130 --> 02:57:42.090
你不是要我使用这些超能力吗
You wanted me to use these gifts, right?


1505
02:57:45.170 --> 02:57:46.670
我就要这么做
That's what I'm gonna do.


1506
02:57:46.840 --> 02:57:48.720
好吧 所以…
Okay. So...


1507
02:57:49.430 --> 02:57:52.680
维克多想和末日母盒 合而为一拯救世界
if Victor wants to try to save the world by fusing with the doom boxes,


1508
02:57:52.890 --> 02:57:55.060
那就让他这么做吧
I say we put him in the doom boxes.


1509
02:57:55.390 --> 02:57:58.190
但要让他这么做就得攻击基地
But getting him in means attacking that base.


1510
02:57:58.350 --> 02:58:00.560
深入地狱向魔鬼与他的军团…
Fighting the devil and his army


1511
02:58:00.730 --> 02:58:01.770
正式开战
in hell.


1512
02:58:01.940 --> 02:58:04.190
这家伙在他摧毁的星球上
I mean, this guy's probably fought


1513
02:58:04.360 --> 02:58:08.320
大概打过成千上万个超级英雄 对吧
hundreds of thousands of other superbeings on the other planets he's destroyed, right?


1514
02:58:08.490 --> 02:58:09.990
我们得假设他都赢了
And we have to assume he's won.


1515
02:58:10.160 --> 02:58:13.280
我才不管他在多少个地狱 打过多少恶魔
I don't care how many demons he's fought in how many hells...


1516
02:58:13.450 --> 02:58:16.950
他没打过我们 团结一致的我们
he's never fought us. Not us united.


1517
02:59:07.420 --> 02:59:09.050
我猜你说"愿意"
Take that as a "yes."


1518
02:59:09.670 --> 02:59:10.510
什么
What?


1519
02:59:13.970 --> 02:59:15.220
那只婚戒
The ring.


1520
02:59:18.930 --> 02:59:20.480
你真的回来了
You're really back.


1521
02:59:53.970 --> 02:59:56.180
我得到第二次机会
I have a second chance, Lo.


1522
02:59:58.470 --> 03:00:00.930
绝对不会白白浪费
And I am not gonna waste it.


1523
03:00:59.200 --> 03:01:00.370
真的是你吗
Are you really you?


1524
03:01:00.530 --> 03:01:02.240
真的是我 妈
I'm really me, Ma.


1525
03:01:20.260 --> 03:01:22.310
听好 妈
Listen, Ma.


1526
03:01:23.890 --> 03:01:25.930
他们让我回来一定有原因
They wanted me back for a reason.


1527
03:01:27.690 --> 03:01:29.230
我得知道为什么
I need to find out why.


1528
03:01:49.370 --> 03:01:50.790
维克多怎么样
How's Victor doing?


1529
03:01:55.170 --> 03:01:57.920
你也知道 他想独处一下
You know, wanted to be by himself.


1530
03:01:59.510 --> 03:02:02.680
我们要求一个刚失去父亲的孩子…
We're asking a kid who just lost his father


1531
03:02:02.850 --> 03:02:05.640
对抗全宇宙最强大的机器
to go up against the most powerful machines in the universe.


1532
03:02:07.480 --> 03:02:08.980
这不公平
It's not fair.


1533
03:02:10.730 --> 03:02:12.360
我以为你不在乎
I thought you didn't care?


1534
03:02:13.770 --> 03:02:15.280
我从来没这么说过
I never said that.


1535
03:02:28.210 --> 03:02:29.620
怎么了
What is it?


1536
03:02:33.540 --> 03:02:38.550
我做过一个梦 不晓得 几乎就像一种预感
I had a dream, like, I don't know, almost like a premonition.


1537
03:02:39.510 --> 03:02:42.300
那是世界末日
It was the end of the world


1538
03:02:42.470 --> 03:02:45.310
巴里·艾伦就在这里
and Barry Allen was right here


1539
03:02:45.470 --> 03:02:49.350
他跟我说 "露易丝·莱恩才是关键"
and he said to me, "Lois Lane is the key."


1540
03:02:52.020 --> 03:02:55.230
对超人来说…她是
She is... to Superman.


1541
03:02:56.280 --> 03:02:57.900
每个人都有心爱的人
Every heart has one.


1542
03:02:58.530 --> 03:03:00.400
我想不只是这样
I think it's something more.


1543
03:03:01.280 --> 03:03:03.160
这是更黑暗的东西
Something darker.


1544
03:03:07.330 --> 03:03:08.330
韦恩少爷
Master Wayne.


1545
03:03:08.500 --> 03:03:10.000
韦恩少爷
Master Wayne!


1546
03:03:10.830 --> 03:03:12.500
你得来看看
You need to see this.


1547
03:03:35.770 --> 03:03:37.480
你修好了
You fixed it.


1548
03:03:37.650 --> 03:03:39.360
它想要飞行
It wanted to fly.


1549
03:03:40.610 --> 03:03:41.950
飞行是它的本能
Flight is its nature.


1550
03:03:42.110 --> 03:03:43.410
也是你的
Yours, too.


1551
03:03:50.200 --> 03:03:52.160
他会来的 阿尔弗雷德 我知道
He'll be here, Alfred, I know it.


1552
03:03:52.330 --> 03:03:53.960
你为何这么肯定
What makes you so sure?


1553
03:03:54.710 --> 03:03:57.290
信念 阿尔弗雷德 信念
Faith, Alfred. Faith.


1554
03:04:19.400 --> 03:04:20.980
终于
At last.


1555
03:04:22.820 --> 03:04:25.530
准备迎接他的到来
Prepare for his arrival.


1556
03:04:27.370 --> 03:04:31.500
我即将得到救赎
My redemption is nigh.


1557
03:04:39.380 --> 03:04:40.840
合而为一
Unite.


1558
03:04:46.010 --> 03:04:48.510
同步化
Synchronize.


1559
03:05:32.850 --> 03:05:35.770
卫星显示他打造了一个防御圆顶
The satellites revealed he's created a defensive dome.


1560
03:05:35.930 --> 03:05:37.100
这是个设计缺陷
It's a design flaw.


1561
03:05:37.270 --> 03:05:39.520
把塔台射倒 圆顶就会崩垮
Take out the tower, the dome will fall.


1562
03:05:39.690 --> 03:05:41.690
敌人不会料到我们正面攻击
The enemy never anticipated a frontal assault.


1563
03:05:41.860 --> 03:05:45.360
是啊 因为他没想到 有人会这么疯狂
Right, probably 'cause he didn't think anyone would be that nuts.


1564
03:05:46.360 --> 03:05:47.650
布鲁斯是对的
Bruce is right.


1565
03:05:47.820 --> 03:05:49.410
我们必须摧毁防御圆顶
We've got to destroy the defensive dome


1566
03:05:49.570 --> 03:05:51.870
在它们同步化之前找到母盒
so we can reach The Unity before it synchronizes.


1567
03:05:52.030 --> 03:05:53.740
要是圆顶没被摧毁呢
What if the dome's not destroyed?


1568
03:05:53.910 --> 03:05:54.910
它一定会被摧毁
It'll be destroyed.


1569
03:05:55.080 --> 03:05:56.710
维克多一旦融入三位一体
Once Victor is linked with The Unity


1570
03:05:57.210 --> 03:06:00.460
有巴里的协助 他就能突破母盒的防御
with Barry's help, he'll break through The Unity's defenses.


1571
03:06:00.630 --> 03:06:02.090
提醒我 我该怎么做
Remind me, how's that again?


1572
03:06:02.250 --> 03:06:03.880
用爱的力量
Uh, with the power of love.


1573
03:06:04.050 --> 03:06:06.670
-巴里 -我得造成能量大爆发
-Barry. -With a catastrophic energy surge.


1574
03:06:06.840 --> 03:06:07.840
很好
Good.


1575
03:06:08.010 --> 03:06:09.890
你得比以前跑得更快
You'll have to run faster than you've ever attempted


1576
03:06:10.050 --> 03:06:12.600
才能产生这么大的电流
to generate a charge of that size.


1577
03:06:12.760 --> 03:06:14.770
然后直接碰触维克多的身体
And then you make physical contact with Victor.


1578
03:06:15.100 --> 03:06:17.980
那股能量应该能让他进入母盒
That force should propel him inside The Unity.


1579
03:06:18.140 --> 03:06:20.020
维克多 之后就靠你了
And, Victor, it's all up to you.


1580
03:06:20.190 --> 03:06:22.940
在它同步化之前把它扯开
Take it apart from the inside before it synchronizes.


1581
03:06:24.520 --> 03:06:26.650
我们终于有了计划
Whew. We actually finally have a plan.


1582
03:06:27.190 --> 03:06:28.900
我们有了计划
We have a plan.


1583
03:06:44.250 --> 03:06:46.300
艾尔之家的标记代表希望
The symbol of the house of El means hope.


1584
03:06:46.460 --> 03:06:48.630
这希望包含了一个基本的信念
Embodied within that hope is the fundamental belief


1585
03:06:48.800 --> 03:06:52.510
那就是每个人都有行善的潜力
in the potential of every person to be a force for good.


1586
03:06:52.680 --> 03:06:53.510
克拉克
Clark...


1587
03:06:53.680 --> 03:06:54.970
那就是你能带给他们的
That's what you can bring them.


1588
03:06:55.140 --> 03:06:57.100
你被送来这里是有原因的
...you were sent here for a reason.


1589
03:06:57.270 --> 03:07:01.140
你将给地球的人类 一个努力达到的理想
You will give the people of Earth an ideal to strive towards.


1590
03:07:01.810 --> 03:07:03.650
就算你必须穷尽一生
And even if it takes you the rest of your life,


1591
03:07:03.810 --> 03:07:07.570
也得尽全力找到你来这里的原因
you owe it to yourself to find out what that reason is.


1592
03:07:07.730 --> 03:07:10.360
他们会犯错 也会失败
They will stumble, they will fall.


1593
03:07:10.530 --> 03:07:11.860
但你必须做出选择
You're gonna have to make a choice.


1594
03:07:12.660 --> 03:07:15.080
他们将与你一起迎向阳光
They will join you in the sun, Kal.


1595
03:07:15.240 --> 03:07:19.200
你必须选择是否要 骄傲地站在全人类面前
A choice of whether to stand proud in front of the human race or not.


1596
03:07:19.370 --> 03:07:22.540
你将帮助他们完成奇迹
You will help them accomplish wonders.


1597
03:07:39.680 --> 03:07:44.190
氪星所有的希望和梦想 都寄托在你身上
All the hopes and dreams of Krypton live in you now.


1598
03:07:44.350 --> 03:07:46.610
我真为你感到骄傲 儿子
I'm so proud of you, son.


1599
03:07:47.940 --> 03:07:49.990
你母亲和我都很爱你
Your mother and I loved you.


1600
03:07:50.650 --> 03:07:54.200
你母亲和我都知道你会改变世界
Your mother and I knew you would change the world.


1601
03:07:55.490 --> 03:07:57.330
你的心受到考验
Your heart was tested.


1602
03:07:58.620 --> 03:08:00.580
我知道这很难 克拉克
I know it's been hard, Clark.


1603
03:08:01.330 --> 03:08:04.250
但你给了他们的世界一个希望
But you gave hope to their world.


1604
03:08:04.420 --> 03:08:07.090
你必须让他们看到你是谁
You need to show them who you are.


1605
03:08:07.790 --> 03:08:09.500
爱他们吧 卡尔·艾尔
Love them, Kal.


1606
03:08:10.130 --> 03:08:12.260
就像我们爱你一样
The way we loved you.


1607
03:08:14.720 --> 03:08:15.840
飞吧 儿子
Fly, son.


1608
03:08:16.890 --> 03:08:18.100
是时候了
It's time.


1609
03:09:21.870 --> 03:09:25.000
我要把塔台射倒 破坏力场圆顶
I'm gonna take out that tower and knock down that shield dome.


1610
03:09:25.160 --> 03:09:26.290
不管你们看到什么
Whatever you see,


1611
03:09:27.620 --> 03:09:29.580
都要按照计划
stick to the plan.


1612
03:09:31.460 --> 03:09:33.380
这就是我把你们聚在一起的原因
It's why I brought you together.


1613
03:10:13.460 --> 03:10:15.210
布鲁斯 撤退 你不会成功的
Bruce, pull back. You're not gonna make it.


1614
03:10:19.010 --> 03:10:21.050
只要敲大声一点
Just have to knock a little louder.


1615
03:10:46.040 --> 03:10:47.620
杀了他
Kill him!


1616
03:10:47.790 --> 03:10:50.540
快去捍卫三位一体
Get to the carriage. Defend The Unity.


1617
03:10:55.840 --> 03:10:56.760
惨了
Oh, shit.


1618
03:11:17.070 --> 03:11:17.990
塔台倒了
The tower's down.


1619
03:11:19.610 --> 03:11:21.030
收到吗
Do you read me?


1620
03:11:21.660 --> 03:11:22.780
收到了
Uh, yeah, loud and clear.


1621
03:11:23.870 --> 03:11:25.240
你没事吗
Are you okay?


1622
03:11:26.490 --> 03:11:29.080
布鲁斯
Bruce? Bruce?


1623
03:11:29.370 --> 03:11:30.250
快去反应炉
Get to the reactor.


1624
03:11:30.410 --> 03:11:32.920
我会尽量把这些怪物引开来
I'll lure as many of these monsters away from you as I can.


1625
03:11:33.080 --> 03:11:33.920
那是什么意思
-What does that mean?


1626
03:11:36.920 --> 03:11:38.920
别担心我 快去找到母盒
Don't worry about me. Get to The Unity.


1627
03:11:41.590 --> 03:11:42.760
它们来了
They're here.


1628
03:11:43.140 --> 03:11:44.050
布鲁斯
Bruce?


1629
03:11:46.970 --> 03:11:48.270
失去讯号
Comm went dead.


1630
03:11:49.980 --> 03:11:51.230
上吧
Let's go.


1631
03:12:30.140 --> 03:12:31.980
跟我来呀 你们这群臭虫
Come on, follow me, you damn insects.


1632
03:13:51.930 --> 03:13:53.100
严重受损
Critical damage.


1633
03:14:33.100 --> 03:14:34.350
你真的发疯了
You really are outta your mind.


1634
03:15:01.250 --> 03:15:02.380
不客气
You're welcome.


1635
03:15:02.540 --> 03:15:03.840
厉害 兄弟
My man.


1636
03:16:36.930 --> 03:16:38.560
放心 我们能搞定
Yeah, we got this.


1637
03:16:38.720 --> 03:16:40.100
你去做该做的事
You go do your thing.


1638
03:17:35.900 --> 03:17:37.410
我猜你就是阿尔弗雷德
I'm assuming you're Alfred.


1639
03:17:39.280 --> 03:17:40.580
肯特少爷
Master Kent.


1640
03:17:42.620 --> 03:17:44.120
他说你会来
He said you'd come.


1641
03:17:45.830 --> 03:17:49.250
希望你没有来得太晚
Now, let's hope you're not too late.


1642
03:18:00.100 --> 03:18:01.180
喂
-Hey!


1643
03:18:10.480 --> 03:18:11.820
记得我吗
Remember me?


1644
03:18:14.360 --> 03:18:15.780
第二回合
Round two?


1645
03:18:16.490 --> 03:18:17.650
好啊
Hell yeah.


1646
03:18:39.180 --> 03:18:40.550
上吧
Shall we?


1647
03:18:41.510 --> 03:18:43.810
告诉我 亚马逊女战士
Tell me, Amazon,


1648
