你对死亡麻木之前 还有多少人会死在你怀里
Because how many can die in your arms before you grow numb to death?


1839
03:46:34.520 --> 03:46:36.400
你说话一点都不小心
That's not very careful.


1840
03:46:37.650 --> 03:46:40.770
你还要看着多少死人的眼睛
And how many dead eyes can you look into


1841
03:46:41.480 --> 03:46:43.860
才会彻底心死
before you die inside yourself?


1842
03:46:44.400 --> 03:46:48.070
我已经心死了很久
I've been dead inside a long time,


1843
03:46:48.240 --> 03:46:50.160
但就连我也有忍耐极限
but even I have a limit.


1844
03:46:50.330 --> 03:46:52.040
你敢跨过那极限 我发誓会…
And if you cross that line, I swear to God, I will...


1845
03:46:52.200 --> 03:46:54.500
你会怎样 布鲁斯杀了我
Before what, Bruce? Kill me?


1846
03:46:55.210 --> 03:46:57.000
你不会杀我
You won't kill me.


1847
03:46:57.870 --> 03:46:59.840
我是你最好的朋友
I'm your best friend.


1848
03:47:00.340 --> 03:47:04.380
而且 谁会摸你的蛋蛋
Besides, who's gonna give you a reach-around?


1849
03:47:06.380 --> 03:47:07.760
反正呢
Anyway,


1850
03:47:09.050 --> 03:47:10.600
你需要我
you need me.


1851
03:47:11.640 --> 03:47:13.140
你…
You


1852
03:47:13.680 --> 03:47:19.310
让她死以后造成的这个世界 需要我帮你恢复原状
need me to help you undo this world you created by letting her die.


1853
03:47:21.900 --> 03:47:23.150
可怜的露易丝
Poor Lois.


1854
03:47:23.940 --> 03:47:26.740
她受尽了折磨
How she suffered so!


1855
03:47:32.620 --> 03:47:34.080
我常常在想
I often wonder


1856
03:47:35.040 --> 03:47:39.170
你在多少个平行时空毁灭世界 老实说…
how many alternate timelines do you destroy the world because...


1857
03:47:40.330 --> 03:47:44.500
都是因为你没种让自己死
frankly, you don't have the cojones to die yourself.


1858
03:47:49.090 --> 03:47:52.890
所以我还是一样比你更成熟
So, as usual, I'll be the bigger man.


1859
03:47:56.730 --> 03:47:58.190
停战吧
A truce,


1860
03:47:59.020 --> 03:48:00.310
布鲁斯
Bruce.


1861
03:48:03.070 --> 03:48:07.150
只要你有这张牌 我们就停战
As long as you have this card, a truce.


1862
03:48:10.200 --> 03:48:13.410
但你只要把它撕成一半 我就很乐意跟你谈谈
But all you have to do is tear it in half and I'm happy to discuss with you


1863
03:48:13.580 --> 03:48:16.580
你为什么要派那个神奇小子
in any way you like, why you sent the Boy Wonder


1864
03:48:18.330 --> 03:48:20.170
去做一个男人的工作
to do a man's job?


1865
03:48:23.590 --> 03:48:25.380
真的很好笑
You know, it's funny


1866
03:48:25.550 --> 03:48:28.590
你竟然敢说有多少人死在我怀里
that you would talk about people who died in my arms


1867
03:48:28.760 --> 03:48:30.470
当我把哈莉·奎茵抱在怀里
because when I held Harley Quinn


1868
03:48:30.630 --> 03:48:33.100
她满身是血 奄奄一息时
and she was bleeding and dying,


1869
03:48:33.260 --> 03:48:36.810
她用最后一口气哀求我
she begged me with her last breath


1870
03:48:36.970 --> 03:48:39.230
当我杀你的时候
that when I killed you,


1871
03:48:39.390 --> 03:48:42.810
别搞错 我一定会他妈的杀了你
and make no mistake, I will fucking kill you...


1872
03:48:42.980 --> 03:48:44.820
她要我慢慢来
that I'd do it slow.


1873
03:48:46.020 --> 03:48:47.990
我会信守这个承诺
I'm gonna honor that promise.


1874
03:49:19.770 --> 03:49:21.350
你真会演戏
Oh. You're good.


1875
03:49:25.650 --> 03:49:27.230
差点就唬住我了
You almost had me.


1876
03:49:46.710 --> 03:49:47.790
我们要躲在哪里
Where are we holing up?


1877
03:49:47.960 --> 03:49:50.210
他永远不会料到的地方
Somewhere he'll never suspect.


1878
03:49:50.670 --> 03:49:53.590
还是觉得带着他是个好主意吗
Still think it was a good idea bringing him along?


1879
03:49:54.680 --> 03:49:56.220
你觉得呢
-what do you think?


1880
03:50:02.310 --> 03:50:03.310
他找到我们了
He's found us.


1881
03:51:32.480 --> 03:51:33.940
我能帮你吗
Can I help you?


1882
03:51:35.320 --> 03:51:38.820
你一定知道达克赛德不会放过地球
I'm sure you know Darkseid is not finished with Earth.


1883
03:51:38.990 --> 03:51:41.990
反生命方程序就在这里
The Anti-Life Equation is here somewhere.


1884
03:51:42.160 --> 03:51:44.950
我们得赶在他之前找到它
We have to find it before he does.


1885
03:51:45.120 --> 03:51:46.830
决战时刻即将到来
There's a war coming.


1886
03:51:47.120 --> 03:51:48.870
我是来帮忙的
And I'm here to help.


1887
03:51:49.040 --> 03:51:51.290
抱歉 你是哪位
I'm sorry, who are you again?


1888
03:51:51.460 --> 03:51:56.550
我有很多名字和很多形体 就像你一样…
I've gone by many names and taken many forms. And like you,


1889
03:51:57.170 --> 03:51:59.800
我发现自己要对这世界负责
I've realized I have a stake in this world


1890
03:51:59.970 --> 03:52:02.430
我也该为它而战了
and it's time I started fighting for it.


1891
03:52:05.970 --> 03:52:08.100
我们是需要帮助
Well, we could definitely use the help.


1892
03:52:08.310 --> 03:52:11.520
所以很高兴你来了
So, glad you're here.


1893
03:52:12.770 --> 03:52:14.940
我没想过会看到地球的守护者
You know, I never thought I'd see the defenders of Earth


1894
03:52:15.110 --> 03:52:17.280
会团结一致 并肩作战
united and fighting as one.


1895
03:52:18.280 --> 03:52:20.660
没有你就不会发生 布鲁斯
It wouldn't have happened without you, Bruce.


1896
03:52:22.120 --> 03:52:24.490
你父母会为你感到骄傲
Your mother and father would be proud.


1897
03:52:25.870 --> 03:52:27.040
希望如此
I hope so.


1898
03:52:33.090 --> 03:52:36.050
我会保持联系
Well, I'll be in touch.


1899
03:52:37.090 --> 03:52:41.130
对了 有些人叫我…
Oh, and some have called me


1900
03:52:41.300 --> 03:52:43.600
火星猎人
the Martian Manhunter.


1901
03:52:51.310 --> 03:52:53.650
我猜我会再见到你
I guess I'll see you around.


1902
03:53:24.090 --> 03:53:30.190
献给秋